INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (4,'Atlantic Grease And Lubricants Is A Proud Industry Leader In High-Performance Lubricants Formulation','atlantic-grease-and-lubricants-is-a-proud-industry-leader-in-high-performance-lubricants-formulation','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"There are only a small number of companies that have the potential to truly dominate the oil industry due to the exceptional quality of their products. A company that satisfies the criteria specified by this criterion is \"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic Grease and Lubricants\",\"bold\":true},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"We maintain a comprehensive inventory of lubricants and greases after they have been approved by the original equipment manufacturer (OEM). This is because it enables us to select the most suitable product for each and every task in the industry and the automotives. We provide our customers with high-quality engine oil, clutch fluid, and brake fluid.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic Grease and Lubricants is committed to adhering to the most rigorous standards. This is the reason why the organization distinguishes itself from its peers in the same sector. AGL designs and manufactures products using only the highest quality components that are presently accessible in order to satisfy the constantly changing needs of its customers.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Additionally, we are perpetually engaged in the development of new products to augment our inventory and conduct ongoing research. This is the reason why the company offers a variety of oils that are not only environmentally friendly but also safe for human consumption.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Our clients enjoy the benefits of our products such as high-quality materials, developments and tested products, and commitments to an excellent and wide range of products for diverse use.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Benefits of Atlantic Grease and Lubricants\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Various products, like hydraulic fluid, gear oil, brake fluid, gear oil, and specialized lubricants, are available. Additionally, we provide a large variety of additional products from collections that are available to purchase. We produce our products for a diverse range of industries, such as the maritime industry, the industrial sector, and the automotive sector. It is important to note that the company highlights the following characteristics and advantages of its products. All these products are made with details of the highest possible quality at all times.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"They are continually developing and testing new formulations to conform to the ever-increasing requirements of their customers. To fulfill their client’s needs, they are committed to delivering products and services of the highest possible quality. The company provides a wide selection of products to cater to the requirements of a wide variety of customers. In addition, the organization offers its consumers with outstanding customer service. \"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Our Products For The Vast Array Of Industrial Use\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Many industries have achieved high performance and success after they have used our products. these industries are marine, industrial and automotive, agriculture and aviation. our wide range of products includes motor oils, gearboxes, brake fluid, hydraulics and specialty lubricants. all these products efficiently lubricate the machines and engines and enable them for efficient working and smooth performance. all our products are carefully designed to meet their needs and demands. AGL also undertakes continued research and uses modern technology to produce premium products. Our efforts help us satisfy our clients’ ever-changing demands.  additionally, our client services are of primary emphasis for us as we are always available for our clients to provide them best solutions for their machine problems. The team of excerpts is always available here to answer your questions at any time of the day and night. they are both competent and expert in their fields to formulate and design the products according to the needs and demands of the customers. \"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Products of AGL\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Products-Of-Atlantic-Grease-And-Lubricants-1024x512.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Products-Of-Atlantic-Grease-And-Lubricants\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Products_Of_Atlantic_Grease_And_Lubricants_1024x512_4bbeb00196.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Products-Of-Atlantic-Grease-And-Lubricants-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Products_Of_Atlantic_Grease_And_Lubricants_1024x512_4bbeb00196\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":12.28,\"sizeInBytes\":12279,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Products_Of_Atlantic_Grease_And_Lubricants_1024x512_4bbeb00196.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Products-Of-Atlantic-Grease-And-Lubricants-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Products_Of_Atlantic_Grease_And_Lubricants_1024x512_4bbeb00196\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":44.12,\"sizeInBytes\":44117,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Products_Of_Atlantic_Grease_And_Lubricants_1024x512_4bbeb00196.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Products-Of-Atlantic-Grease-And-Lubricants-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Products_Of_Atlantic_Grease_And_Lubricants_1024x512_4bbeb00196\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":85.9,\"sizeInBytes\":85903,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Products_Of_Atlantic_Grease_And_Lubricants_1024x512_4bbeb00196.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Products-Of-Atlantic-Grease-And-Lubricants-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Products_Of_Atlantic_Grease_And_Lubricants_1024x512_4bbeb00196\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":133.87,\"sizeInBytes\":133870,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Products_Of_Atlantic_Grease_And_Lubricants_1024x512_4bbeb00196.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Products_Of_Atlantic_Grease_And_Lubricants_1024x512_4bbeb00196\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":194.35,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-07T10:40:22.008Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-07T10:40:53.007Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The company Atlantic Grease & Lubricants manufactures a wide variety of lubricants and greases of superior quality, including the following:\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Automotive Lubricants:\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"This category of products is designed to meet the needs of a diverse array of automobile applications, like passenger cars, pickups, and sport utility vehicles (SUVs). We provide exceptional protection and performance, and we help with maintaining engines so that they continue operation in a smooth and efficient manner.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Super Synthetic Sae 0w40 Api Sn\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Fully Synthetic Neoteric Ultra 10w40 Sp\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Synthech Ultra Super Motor Oil Sae 5w-30 Api Sl\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Synthech Ultra Super Motor Oil Sae 5w-40 Api Sn/Cf\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Ultra Super Synthetic Engine Oil Sae 5w-40 Api Sp\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic X Turbo Plus Semi Syn Deo\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Industrial Lubricants:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Our items are utilized in a wide range of industrial applications, including heavy machinery and equipment at various levels. We offer improved lubrication and protection and contribute to extending the lifespan of machinery and equipment.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Air Compressor Oil (Synthetic)\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Transformer Oil U\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Transformer Oil Type II\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Circulating Oils\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Chain Oil: High Temperature, Synthetic\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Marine Lubricants:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"These materials are designed to be used in marine applications, such as boats, yachts, and other types of watercraft. Moreover, we contribute to the prevention of corrosion and wear, in addition to providing outstanding performance and protection.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Trunk Piston Engine Oil\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Premium Plus 2-Cycle Outboard 2-Stroke Engine Oil\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Marine HD Mono-Grade Marine Diesel Engine Oil\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Marine Cylinder Oil (CYL)\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Marine System Oil\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Grease:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Bearings, gears, and other moving parts can all benefit from the grease lubrication. We contribute to the formation of a thick and viscous layer that helps to decrease wear and friction. Among the many types of greases that Atlantic Grease & Lubricants provides, some of the options available are synthetic grease, molybdenum disulfide grease, and lithium grease.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Zero Sodium Grease\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Calcium Grease MP\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Lithium Wheel Bearing Grease\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Complex Grease: Lithium-Based\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Atlantic Open Gear Compound\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Every product is designed with the use of cutting-edge technology and components of the highest possible quality in our production process. We are subjected to stringent testing to guarantee that we meet or surpass the standards set by the industry. We are dedicated to providing our customers with the highest-quality products and services that are available under any circumstances.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"If you are ready to experience the difference, let that happen by using our products. You can simply go to the designated page or products and buy from there. If you are looking for more information about what we have to offer, you can call us.\"}]}]','2024-08-07 10:41:28.244000','2024-08-07 11:06:49.212000','2024-08-07 10:42:34.393000',2,2,'2024-06-25'),(5,'In The Ever-Evolving Automotive Market, There Is A Growth Opportunity For Lubricant Companies','in-the-ever-evolving-automotive-market-there-is-a-growth-opportunity-for-lubricant-companies','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"There has been a lot of change in the automotive market. We are still seeing significant shifts from manual cars to electrical vehicles, but the market continues to dominate. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The electric vehicle revolution isn’t just about new cars – it demands a completely new line of fluids, especially from lubricant companies in the UAE.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The manufacturers are being forced to reconsider their entire strategy as a result of the demands for longer-lasting lubricants, stricter emissions rules, and the electrification of vehicles. To build strong relationships with EV manufacturers now is a smart move for the lube industry. It is possible that those who remain stagnant and continue to rely on the same old techniques may be left behind.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"To tell you the truth, changes are rarely comfortable. With that being said, the good news is that this disruption presents a big opportunity for lubricant firms that are prepared to be brave and think outside the box (so to speak).\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Can you design lubricants that combat friction in electric motors, and boost efficiency unlike anything on the market? How about coolants precisely engineered to protect and optimize battery packs? Specializing in these cutting-edge technologies isn’t just a competitive advantage, it’s a ticket to explosive growth alongside the surging electric vehicle market.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"If you want to stay ahead of the curve, you should concentrate on the following:\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Give Your Core Products A Second Thought\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The electric vehicle market is booming, but that doesn’t mean conventional lubricants are obsolete. However, the demand is changing. To stay competitive, it’s time to focus on creating next-generation formulas that cater to a changing automotive landscape. They need to prioritize lubricants that are designed to boost fuel efficiency, reduce emissions, and extend the time between oil changes. This approach won’t just make your products more attractive to eco-conscious customers, but it’ll also benefit their wallets by reducing the need for frequent lubricant changes.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Get A Head Start On The Electrification Process\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"E-fluids are a completely different game. Establish early partnerships with electric vehicle manufacturers in order to obtain an understanding of the specific requirements they have. Is it possible for lubricant manufacturers in the UAE to create oils that are dedicated to electric motors and that reduce friction while also improving efficiency? Or coolants that are specifically designed to meet the requirements of battery packs? Companies that become specialists in these specialized technologies are in a position to experience significant growth as the electric vehicle market continues to expand. \"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Facts Are On Your Side:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Lubricant technology has been vast and is becoming smarter. Through the use of sensors and analysis, opportunities for predictive maintenance are being discovered. In addition to the items you sell, would it be possible for you to provide a service that checks the state of the oil and identifies probable equipment faults before they trigger expensive breakdowns? It is because of this that you are transformed from a seller of commodities into a reliable partner for your clients. \"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Why Sustainability Is Important:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Products that are environmentally responsible are becoming increasingly in demand from both consumers and industries. Invest in research and development to improve the performance of bio-based lubricants. You might also investigate ways to make your production procedures and packaging more environmentally friendly. Having the ability to market your lubricants as “green” allows you to reach new client segments and brings you in line with broader industry trends. \"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Increase The Number Of Products You Offer:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Lubricants on their own might not be sufficient for success over the long term. Would it be possible for you to diversify into similar products? Logical expansions include speciality greases, performance enhancers, and even industrial cleaners. Others include industrial machine lubricants. In addition to being a supplier of oil, the objective is to develop into a provider of all kinds of solutions. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It is essential to keep in mind that there is no answer that is universally applicable. The most effective methods will fit the lubricant’ company’s weaknesses and the market that it intends to serve. The most important thing is to develop good relationships with consumers in order to comprehend the problems they face. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The world of lubricants is unquestionably undergoing change. In spite of this, businesses have the potential to not only endure but also thrive in this exciting new era if they are willing to embrace innovation and engage in rigorous planning. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Since the market for lubricants is experiencing rapid change, businesses need to take decisive action. Planning that is slow and careful is not appropriate at this moment. Instead, it is important for survival to develop daring competitive strategies that are concentrated on extending beyond established product lines.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Emerging Markets And Premiumization Of Products And Services\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Emerging-Markets-And-Premiumization-Of-Products-And-Services-1024x512.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Emerging-Markets-And-Premiumization-Of-Products-And-Services-1024x512.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Emerging_Markets_And_Premiumization_Of_Products_And_Services_1024x512_e154f81cf1.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Emerging-Markets-And-Premiumization-Of-Products-And-Services-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Emerging_Markets_And_Premiumization_Of_Products_And_Services_1024x512_e154f81cf1\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":11.67,\"sizeInBytes\":11671,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Emerging_Markets_And_Premiumization_Of_Products_And_Services_1024x512_e154f81cf1.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Emerging-Markets-And-Premiumization-Of-Products-And-Services-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Emerging_Markets_And_Premiumization_Of_Products_And_Services_1024x512_e154f81cf1\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":39.47,\"sizeInBytes\":39474,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Emerging_Markets_And_Premiumization_Of_Products_And_Services_1024x512_e154f81cf1.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Emerging-Markets-And-Premiumization-Of-Products-And-Services-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Emerging_Markets_And_Premiumization_Of_Products_And_Services_1024x512_e154f81cf1\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":75.44,\"sizeInBytes\":75442,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Emerging_Markets_And_Premiumization_Of_Products_And_Services_1024x512_e154f81cf1.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Emerging-Markets-And-Premiumization-Of-Products-And-Services-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Emerging_Markets_And_Premiumization_Of_Products_And_Services_1024x512_e154f81cf1\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":116.66,\"sizeInBytes\":116659,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Emerging_Markets_And_Premiumization_Of_Products_And_Services_1024x512_e154f81cf1.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Emerging_Markets_And_Premiumization_Of_Products_And_Services_1024x512_e154f81cf1\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":127.32,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-07T11:15:04.994Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-07T11:15:04.994Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The development of higher-margin lube products, particularly the transition toward branded synthetics in the rapidly expanding road-transport sector, is where the lubricant business is headed in terms of profit in the future. Invest more resources into the development of these premium lubricants, with a particular focus on the tremendous growth potential of Latin America, Asia, and Africa among other regions.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The plan of action is as follows:\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Invest significantly in research and development in order to develop specialized, high-performance synthetics that may fetch premium prices. Innovate at the expense of profit. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"An aggressive expansion strategy would be to pursue growth by means of strategic acquisitions, the development of new markets, or the construction of your own assets. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"One way to accomplish this is by utilizing your existing network to reach locations that have not yet been exploited or by locating powerful distributors for market entry.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Understand How to Adapt to a Changing Environment \"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"A strategy that is successful must be able to foresee disturbances and deal with them head-on. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Even if the price of electric vehicle batteries continues to decrease, lubricant businesses have two options to overcome this obstacle: \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Tap into the larger electric vehicle market that encompasses more than simply passenger cars. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Diversify beyond batteries. Commercial vehicles, heavy-duty transportation, and other industries that have varying requirements for lubrication are included in this category.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Innovate Around the Electric Vehicle:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Innovate-Around-the-Electric-Vehicle-1024x512.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Innovate-Around-the-Electric-Vehicle-1024x512.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Innovate_Around_the_Electric_Vehicle_1024x512_4c920e3058.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Innovate-Around-the-Electric-Vehicle-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Innovate_Around_the_Electric_Vehicle_1024x512_4c920e3058\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":10.55,\"sizeInBytes\":10547,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Innovate_Around_the_Electric_Vehicle_1024x512_4c920e3058.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Innovate-Around-the-Electric-Vehicle-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Innovate_Around_the_Electric_Vehicle_1024x512_4c920e3058\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":65.42,\"sizeInBytes\":65420,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Innovate_Around_the_Electric_Vehicle_1024x512_4c920e3058.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Innovate-Around-the-Electric-Vehicle-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Innovate_Around_the_Electric_Vehicle_1024x512_4c920e3058\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":34.4,\"sizeInBytes\":34399,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Innovate_Around_the_Electric_Vehicle_1024x512_4c920e3058.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Innovate-Around-the-Electric-Vehicle-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Innovate_Around_the_Electric_Vehicle_1024x512_4c920e3058\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":99.91,\"sizeInBytes\":99913,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Innovate_Around_the_Electric_Vehicle_1024x512_4c920e3058.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Innovate_Around_the_Electric_Vehicle_1024x512_4c920e3058\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":110.01,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-07T11:17:42.274Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-07T11:17:42.274Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Don’t restrict yourself to conventional lubricants. Take advantage of the chance to produce innovative goods, such as specialized battery coolants, that are specially designed by the oilmanufacturing company UAE to meet the requirements that are unique to electric vehicles.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Why Atlantic Grease and Lubricants FZC strategy is a good one: because this reduces reliance on any one particular technology or market area by spreading risk solutions across multiple markets. the oil and grease manufacturers can be at the forefront of the electric vehicles market which positions you as a leader rather than merely a follower of the business movement.\"}]}]','2024-08-07 11:19:02.095000','2024-08-07 11:19:37.118000','2024-08-07 11:19:37.113000',2,2,'2024-05-08'),(6,'What Are The Four API GL Performance Test Levels For Manual Transmission Fluids?','what-are-the-four-api-gl-performance-test-levels-for-manual-transmission-fluids','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Manual transmission oil, or MTFs, is extensively used in manual automotive transmissions and their transaxles. Manual transmission oils account for 75% of the automotive gear oil market in Europe. However, the remaining 25% account for the automatic transmission fluids.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Before gear oil or transmission fluids can be used in gears, they must undergo a series of tests to ensure they meet certain performance standards. These tests, like the SAE J 2360, evaluate the oils’ ability to withstand high rotational speed, shock loading, and high working temperatures. \"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Four Different Test Levels For Manual Transmission Fluids\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Transmission oils have been evaluated according to a set of criteria defined by the American Petroleum Institute. These criteria are based on the performance of the transmission oils as well as the applications that they are designed to be used for. For the goal of ensuring that the oils are efficient and capable of preserving gears from wear and tear, as well as that they fulfill the specific requirements of a variety of applications, these guidelines offer help to both the manufacturers and the consumers. \"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Understanding Manual Transmission Fluid Tests and Standards\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"A series of tests, including the L-42 test, is performed on the fluids that are used in manual transmission vehicles. As a consequence of this test, the condition of the vehicle’s rear axle has been demonstrated. When oil is applied to the entire back axle, it causes the axle to spin at high speeds, subjects the axle to stress loading, and runs at greater temperatures while the test is being conducted. The results of the tests are an important factor to consider when selecting an oil and assessing whether or not the oil can preserve the gears from wear and strain. Other tests are:\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"API GL-1: This particular oil performance level test is designed for use in manual gearboxes that do not come equipped with synchronizers.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"AP-GL-4 These tests are designated for manual gearboxes that are equipped with synchronizers.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"API GL-5: This oil performance level test is intended for use with manual gearboxes that are subjected to high-performance gear tests while operating in harsh environments.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"MT-1: this is for the engines that are designed to be used off-road to be evaluated.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"On the other hand, it is essential to keep in mind that API GL performance levels are not meant to serve as a substitute for reading the recommendations provided by the car manufacturer.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The API performance levels for manual transmission fluids (MTFs) and their key properties.\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"The-API-performance-levels-for-manual-transmission-fluids-MTFs-and-their-key-properties-1024x512.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"The-API-performance-levels-for-manual-transmission-fluids-MTFs-and-their-key-properties-1024x512.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/The_API_performance_levels_for_manual_transmission_fluids_MT_Fs_and_their_key_properties_1024x512_738ba62e7f.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_The-API-performance-levels-for-manual-transmission-fluids-MTFs-and-their-key-properties-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_The_API_performance_levels_for_manual_transmission_fluids_MT_Fs_and_their_key_properties_1024x512_738ba62e7f\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":7.13,\"sizeInBytes\":7126,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_The_API_performance_levels_for_manual_transmission_fluids_MT_Fs_and_their_key_properties_1024x512_738ba62e7f.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_The-API-performance-levels-for-manual-transmission-fluids-MTFs-and-their-key-properties-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_The_API_performance_levels_for_manual_transmission_fluids_MT_Fs_and_their_key_properties_1024x512_738ba62e7f\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":51.85,\"sizeInBytes\":51849,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_The_API_performance_levels_for_manual_transmission_fluids_MT_Fs_and_their_key_properties_1024x512_738ba62e7f.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_The-API-performance-levels-for-manual-transmission-fluids-MTFs-and-their-key-properties-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_The_API_performance_levels_for_manual_transmission_fluids_MT_Fs_and_their_key_properties_1024x512_738ba62e7f\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":35.43,\"sizeInBytes\":35432,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_The_API_performance_levels_for_manual_transmission_fluids_MT_Fs_and_their_key_properties_1024x512_738ba62e7f.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_The-API-performance-levels-for-manual-transmission-fluids-MTFs-and-their-key-properties-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_The_API_performance_levels_for_manual_transmission_fluids_MT_Fs_and_their_key_properties_1024x512_738ba62e7f\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":20.1,\"sizeInBytes\":20098,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_The_API_performance_levels_for_manual_transmission_fluids_MT_Fs_and_their_key_properties_1024x512_738ba62e7f.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"The_API_performance_levels_for_manual_transmission_fluids_MT_Fs_and_their_key_properties_1024x512_738ba62e7f\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":55.29,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-07T11:26:52.379Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-07T11:26:52.379Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In addition, in addition to the API GL-1, GL-2, GL-3, GL-4, and GL-5 that have been stated above, there is an additional level that is referred to as API GL-5(LS) or GL-5+.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"This degree of condition is met by these gear lubricants, which have unique additives that prevent “stick-slip” from occurring.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic’s gear oils are the API GL-4/GL-5 oils, which are also known as GL-4+. These gear oils are used extensively in the manufacturing of MTFs. Due to the fact that these oils are meant to be utilized in a wide variety of applications, they are an excellent option for a large number of people who use automobiles and drivers.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The FZG A/8.3/90 gear scuffing test is yet another critical test that must be performed. This test is carried out to determine whether or not the oil is capable of preventing gear scuffing, which is a form of wear that can result in gear failure. During the FZG A/8.3/90 test, special test spur gears are utilized, and the circumstances are carefully monitored and controlled. The outcomes of this test contribute to the determination of how well the oil can prevent gears from becoming scratched.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Gear Oil Testing is a Critical Part of manufacturers\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"These tests allow producers to verify that their gear oils are of the highest quality and performance requirements by ensuring that they meet the criteria and standards. By doing so, cars are protected from the effects of wear and tear, and their operation is made more streamlined and energy-efficient.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When it comes to things like automobile engines, testing fancy new lubricants may be quite costly. That is why scientists are constantly looking for ways to do it that are both cheaper and faster. However, the objective is to achieve satisfactory outcomes without incurring the large costs associated with conventional testing procedures.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It is of utmost importance to evaluate gear oil manual transmission fluids. There are a variety of organizations that are continually creating new methods to evaluate the effectiveness of these oils in protecting against things like significant wear and tear. Additionally, to guarantee the accuracy of the outcomes, they make use of specific machines and processes.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Continued Refinement of Gear Oil Testing\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"The-Continued-Refinement-of-Gear-Oil-Testing-1024x512.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"The-Continued-Refinement-of-Gear-Oil-Testing-1024x512.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/The_Continued_Refinement_of_Gear_Oil_Testing_1024x512_87ce768707.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_The-Continued-Refinement-of-Gear-Oil-Testing-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_The_Continued_Refinement_of_Gear_Oil_Testing_1024x512_87ce768707\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":9.22,\"sizeInBytes\":9224,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_The_Continued_Refinement_of_Gear_Oil_Testing_1024x512_87ce768707.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_The-Continued-Refinement-of-Gear-Oil-Testing-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_The_Continued_Refinement_of_Gear_Oil_Testing_1024x512_87ce768707\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":48.13,\"sizeInBytes\":48132,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_The_Continued_Refinement_of_Gear_Oil_Testing_1024x512_87ce768707.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_The-Continued-Refinement-of-Gear-Oil-Testing-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_The_Continued_Refinement_of_Gear_Oil_Testing_1024x512_87ce768707\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":72.04,\"sizeInBytes\":72039,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_The_Continued_Refinement_of_Gear_Oil_Testing_1024x512_87ce768707.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_The-Continued-Refinement-of-Gear-Oil-Testing-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_The_Continued_Refinement_of_Gear_Oil_Testing_1024x512_87ce768707\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":27.36,\"sizeInBytes\":27359,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_The_Continued_Refinement_of_Gear_Oil_Testing_1024x512_87ce768707.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"The_Continued_Refinement_of_Gear_Oil_Testing_1024x512_87ce768707\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":78.64,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-07T11:28:02.492Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-07T11:28:02.492Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"This new test even works on parts with special coatings that are designed to reduce wear. This is a big deal for industries where parts absolutely have to last a long time and stay in tip-top shape. Being able to test how well these coatings work is super helpful.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Scientists are always finding new ways to test lubricants. The goal is to get good information that helps companies make better oils for our cars, machines, and tools and do it all without breaking the bank on expensive testing.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Factors To Look For Other Than API Testing\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Other than the testing, there are some other factors to consider when choosing the best manual transmission fluid. These are:\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"One factor to take into account is the viscosity of the fluid. One approach to explain the resistance to flow that a fluid possesses is by referring to its viscosity. The appropriate viscosity for a particular gearbox is defined by the temperature range in which it will be used. Different manual gearboxes require different viscosities of fluid, and their ideal viscosity is determined by the temperature range.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Consider the additive package that is contained within the fluid as well. The additive package that is contained within transmission fluid serves the purpose of preventing rust, corrosion, and wear and tear. If specific additives are used, it is possible to improve the performance of fluids when they are exposed to cold temperatures.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It is critical that you examine the specifications provided by the manufacturer to ensure that the manual transmission fluid you use is compatible with the transmission. You can find the additive package and viscosity that are suitable for the gearbox in the specifications provided by the manufacturer.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When choosing fluid for your vehicle, it is important to be sure to follow these criteria in order to get the most out of your manual transmission.\"}]}]','2024-08-07 11:30:59.488000','2024-08-07 11:31:03.240000','2024-08-07 11:31:03.237000',2,2,'2024-05-29'),(7,'A Greener Shade Of Automotive Industrial Lubricant Trends in 2024','a-greener-shade-of-automotive-industrial-lubricant-trends-in-2024','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Countries that work in the oil business can benefit from saving used lubricants. It’s becoming more and more popular to recycle and reuse them as a source of extra energy, even though they are considered toxic trash because they contain heavy metals and poisonous organic substances. The method is the least expensive, but it also causes the most damage to the earth. Authorities are putting money into saving tools that can be used on a large scale. A valuable substance called bitumen can be made from the deadly, acidic sludge that this process creates. Not only is this change possible from an economic point of view, but it also poses much less of a threat to the environment, which is a big step toward creating more environmentally friendly practices.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Lubricant business is changing all across the world. Professionals in this field can maintain one step ahead of the competition and can set themselves up to be constantly successful.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"A variety of factors, including the epidemic and the need for products that operate better, are driving a moment of amazing change in the worldwide lubricants market.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"There is a rapid shift occurring in the future of mobility. How we think about transportation is being transformed as a result of population increase, urbanization, and the introduction of new technology. There is a possibility that some developments, such as CASE technology (connected, autonomous, shared, and electric), will transform personal automobiles. Additionally, initiatives to reduce carbon emissions and promote sustainability are gaining momentum, which has important repercussions for the lubricants business across all types of applications.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Lubricants Sector Navigates New Frontiers in Sustainability and Performance\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Although there have been advancements achieved in terms of sustainability within the lubricant sector, there are still fresh problems and possibilities on the horizon. As a result of European rules that are attempting to reduce the pollutants produced by vehicles, thinner engine oils such as SAE 0W-20 are gradually becoming more popular. Due to the fact that this change confronts the sector with both obstacles and possibilities, it is necessary for the industry to innovate and adapt in order to fulfill the demand that is always changing.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The lubricants sector is undergoing transformations as a result of newly enacted rules. It is the goal of the standards known as “in-service verification” to ensure that CO2 performance is maintained throughout the lifetime of a vehicle. This has resulted in certain original equipment manufacturers (OEMs) requiring the same engine oil standards over the entirety of the vehicle’s lifespan. The new emissions regulations that the EPA has implemented for cars manufactured between 2027 and 2032 have also been the impetus for the creation of ILSAC GF-7, which has considerable enhancements to its performance. The industry will devote its attention during the year 2024 to demonstrating the technologies that will allow for these enhancements.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Lubricant Industry Adapts to a Multi-Fuel Future\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Lubricant-Industry-Adapts-to-a-Multi-Fuel-Future-1024x512.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Lubricant-Industry-Adapts-to-a-Multi-Fuel-Future-1024x512.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Lubricant_Industry_Adapts_to_a_Multi_Fuel_Future_1024x512_67a017e5c8.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Lubricant-Industry-Adapts-to-a-Multi-Fuel-Future-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Lubricant_Industry_Adapts_to_a_Multi_Fuel_Future_1024x512_67a017e5c8\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":10.74,\"sizeInBytes\":10743,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Lubricant_Industry_Adapts_to_a_Multi_Fuel_Future_1024x512_67a017e5c8.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Lubricant-Industry-Adapts-to-a-Multi-Fuel-Future-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Lubricant_Industry_Adapts_to_a_Multi_Fuel_Future_1024x512_67a017e5c8\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":34.95,\"sizeInBytes\":34949,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Lubricant_Industry_Adapts_to_a_Multi_Fuel_Future_1024x512_67a017e5c8.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Lubricant-Industry-Adapts-to-a-Multi-Fuel-Future-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Lubricant_Industry_Adapts_to_a_Multi_Fuel_Future_1024x512_67a017e5c8\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":103.63,\"sizeInBytes\":103630,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Lubricant_Industry_Adapts_to_a_Multi_Fuel_Future_1024x512_67a017e5c8.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Lubricant-Industry-Adapts-to-a-Multi-Fuel-Future-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Lubricant_Industry_Adapts_to_a_Multi_Fuel_Future_1024x512_67a017e5c8\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":66.72,\"sizeInBytes\":66718,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Lubricant_Industry_Adapts_to_a_Multi_Fuel_Future_1024x512_67a017e5c8.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Lubricant_Industry_Adapts_to_a_Multi_Fuel_Future_1024x512_67a017e5c8\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":146.96,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-08T07:43:57.766Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-08T07:43:57.766Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The car lubricant and grease sector is facing problems as a result of the proliferation of innovative mobility options and alternative fuels now available. The automotive industry is investigating several fuels, including hydrogen, natural gas, biofuels, and electric fuels, all of which have their own specific lubricating needs. Oxidation and cleanliness are two issues that arise while dealing with biofuels, for example. Although they are recognized since biofuels have been used for a long time, the fact that their popularity is expanding, particularly in Latin America, which is rich in biofuels, means that lubricant marketers need to adjust in order to maintain their competitive edge.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"New Mobility and Sustainability Rules Challenge Lubricant Industry\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"We are already witnessing the advent of new types of mobility, which will provide further issues for lubricants. This is occurring concurrently with the implementation of new restrictions for sustainability.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When it comes to internal combustion engines (ICE), original equipment manufacturers (OEMs) are investigating a broad variety of alternative fuels that have superior environmental and sustainability characteristics than conventional fossil fuels. In addition to gasoline and diesel fuel, these include hydrogen, natural gas, biofuels, and e-fuels, which are frequently referred to as synthetic gasoline. Each of these fuels may have totally different needs for the lubricant than gas or diesel fuel.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The production of biofuels, for instance, is fraught with difficulties including oxidation and cleanliness. These difficulties are well acknowledged due to the fact that biofuels have been around for a considerable amount of time. In spite of this, we may assume that the utilization of biofuels will continue to expand well beyond the year 2024, notably in Latin America, where there is a large supply of biofuels produced domestically. Marketers of automotive lubricants in UAE who want to participate in these areas need to be ready for the competition.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Innovation in Lubricants Promises Efficiency Gains and Environmental Benefits\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Innovation-in-Lubricants-Promises-Efficiency-Gains-and-Environmental-Benefits.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Innovation-in-Lubricants-Promises-Efficiency-Gains-and-Environmental-Benefits.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Innovation_in_Lubricants_Promises_Efficiency_Gains_and_Environmental_Benefits_dcb80ad8b7.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Innovation-in-Lubricants-Promises-Efficiency-Gains-and-Environmental-Benefits.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Innovation_in_Lubricants_Promises_Efficiency_Gains_and_Environmental_Benefits_dcb80ad8b7\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":9.21,\"sizeInBytes\":9206,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Innovation_in_Lubricants_Promises_Efficiency_Gains_and_Environmental_Benefits_dcb80ad8b7.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Innovation-in-Lubricants-Promises-Efficiency-Gains-and-Environmental-Benefits.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Innovation_in_Lubricants_Promises_Efficiency_Gains_and_Environmental_Benefits_dcb80ad8b7\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":29.18,\"sizeInBytes\":29179,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Innovation_in_Lubricants_Promises_Efficiency_Gains_and_Environmental_Benefits_dcb80ad8b7.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Innovation-in-Lubricants-Promises-Efficiency-Gains-and-Environmental-Benefits.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Innovation_in_Lubricants_Promises_Efficiency_Gains_and_Environmental_Benefits_dcb80ad8b7\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":54.36,\"sizeInBytes\":54358,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Innovation_in_Lubricants_Promises_Efficiency_Gains_and_Environmental_Benefits_dcb80ad8b7.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Innovation-in-Lubricants-Promises-Efficiency-Gains-and-Environmental-Benefits.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Innovation_in_Lubricants_Promises_Efficiency_Gains_and_Environmental_Benefits_dcb80ad8b7\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":84.48,\"sizeInBytes\":84478,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Innovation_in_Lubricants_Promises_Efficiency_Gains_and_Environmental_Benefits_dcb80ad8b7.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Innovation_in_Lubricants_Promises_Efficiency_Gains_and_Environmental_Benefits_dcb80ad8b7\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":116.9,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-08T07:54:55.337Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-08T07:54:55.337Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Conventional lubricants, despite their dependability, have several undesirable characteristics. Furthermore, they have a shorter lifespan, which necessitates frequent oil changes, and they are less stable when exposed to severe temperatures. Recent developments in lubrication technology have resulted in the creation of synthetic and bio-based replacements to the traditional lubricant. New lubricants are being developed with the intention of overcoming the constraints of traditional lubricants by providing enhanced performance, increased efficiency, and possibly significantly longer lifespans. This trend toward improved lubricants holds the potential of a future that is both more environmentally friendly and more efficient for the automobile industry.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"From Oil Changes to Overhauls, The Synthetic Revolution in Lubricant Technology\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In the course of time, lubricant technology has seen substantial development. In the beginning, mineral-based oils were refined in order to increase their lubricating capabilities so that they could be used in automobiles. But the most significant development was the advent of synthetic lubricants, which were used in the industry. Automotive lubricants that were developed in a laboratory performed better than conventional oils in a number of ways. These products provided improved stability even when subjected to high temperatures, decreased friction, and greater protection against wear and tear. Furthermore, synthetic lubricants enhanced fuel efficiency and prolonged the life of the engine, in addition to its performance benefits. The automotive lubricants manufacturers saw a significant turning point as a result of this transformation, which supported the industry’s development of cars that were more fuel efficient and had a longer lifespan.\"}]}]','2024-08-08 07:56:49.182000','2024-08-08 07:56:52.041000','2024-08-08 07:56:52.035000',2,2,'2024-06-28'),(8,'Automotive Specialties Like The Coolants’ Potential To Revolutionize Engine Cooling Systems','automotive-specialties-like-the-coolants-potential-to-revolutionize-engine-cooling-systems','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The automotive industry is always trying to make engines run better while also making them smaller and lighter in weight. This has led to a significant increase in power density. The results are smaller bonnet spaces and insufficient heat dissipation rates in radiators. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The engine loses almost 35% of its energy as heat in combustion. This heat should be dissipated equally so that the engine stays at the right temperature and gives 100% performance completely.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"There are several reasons why engines get too hot. Modern engines are small, and when they are moving, the process creates very high temperatures and pressures. It is hard for the heat to dissipate. The small bonnet in modern cars makes it harder for air to flow and heat to escape, which leads to high engine temperatures.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When the car engine gets too hot, bad things happen. For example, insufficient heat dissipation leads to engine lubrication breakdown, which further results in wear and friction between engine parts. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Over time, this can cause engine parts to break down too soon and need immediate maintenance, which could be costly.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It could be worse. The engine parts can break down because they get too hot, which weakens their structure and furthers the risk of a catastrophic failure.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Innovative Solutions For Efficient Engine Cooling Systems\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Engineers have contributed to combating this issue. They came up with the solution to make the radiator bigger and add more fans. They have done perfectly to deal with the overheating systems.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"However, it needs to be considered from a broader perspective with coolant manufacturers as well. Here is a further elaboration of the solution to this problem in advanced lubrication specialties. \"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Role of Coolant Fluid in Engine Cooling\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The radiator is very important for keeping the engine cool, but the coolant fluid that flows through the system has a big impact on how well it works. The main job of coolant, which is also sometimes called antifreeze, is to move engine heat into the air effectively. To make coolant work better, it needs to have additives.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Viscosity index improvers must be added to keep the engine well-oiled even when it’s going at high temperatures. By cutting down on friction and wear, these chemicals make the engine last longer.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Companies that make coolants for cars should also work closely with engineers to make products that improve the overall performance of cooling systems. Modern coolants should be made with the goal of transferring heat as efficiently as possible. Lubricant technology and studies that are always getting better are the keys to reaching this goal.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Ethylene glycol being used in cooling recipes is one example of this kind of change. With this added, the fluid can take in and let go of heat from the engine much better. Modern engines use heat, but these additives can handle it in coolants.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Potential of Nanofluids for Enhanced Automotive Cooling Systems\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"The-Potential-of-Nanofluids-for-Enhanced-Automotive-Cooling-Systems-1024x512.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"The-Potential-of-Nanofluids-for-Enhanced-Automotive-Cooling-Systems-1024x512.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/The_Potential_of_Nanofluids_for_Enhanced_Automotive_Cooling_Systems_1024x512_4ab51979b0.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_The-Potential-of-Nanofluids-for-Enhanced-Automotive-Cooling-Systems-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_The_Potential_of_Nanofluids_for_Enhanced_Automotive_Cooling_Systems_1024x512_4ab51979b0\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":9.87,\"sizeInBytes\":9867,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_The_Potential_of_Nanofluids_for_Enhanced_Automotive_Cooling_Systems_1024x512_4ab51979b0.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_The-Potential-of-Nanofluids-for-Enhanced-Automotive-Cooling-Systems-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_The_Potential_of_Nanofluids_for_Enhanced_Automotive_Cooling_Systems_1024x512_4ab51979b0\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":29.57,\"sizeInBytes\":29573,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_The_Potential_of_Nanofluids_for_Enhanced_Automotive_Cooling_Systems_1024x512_4ab51979b0.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_The-Potential-of-Nanofluids-for-Enhanced-Automotive-Cooling-Systems-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_The_Potential_of_Nanofluids_for_Enhanced_Automotive_Cooling_Systems_1024x512_4ab51979b0\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":80.84,\"sizeInBytes\":80837,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_The_Potential_of_Nanofluids_for_Enhanced_Automotive_Cooling_Systems_1024x512_4ab51979b0.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_The-Potential-of-Nanofluids-for-Enhanced-Automotive-Cooling-Systems-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_The_Potential_of_Nanofluids_for_Enhanced_Automotive_Cooling_Systems_1024x512_4ab51979b0\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":53.51,\"sizeInBytes\":53505,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_The_Potential_of_Nanofluids_for_Enhanced_Automotive_Cooling_Systems_1024x512_4ab51979b0.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"The_Potential_of_Nanofluids_for_Enhanced_Automotive_Cooling_Systems_1024x512_4ab51979b0\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":87.91,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-08T08:18:24.743Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-08T08:18:24.743Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In the automobile industry, the goal of better efficiency and performance goes beyond just making the engine stronger. Moving heat around is an important part of keeping the engine at the right temperature, and new developments in cooling technology have made a lot of new options possible.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"One area that is being looked into is the use of nanofluids, which are fluids that contain nanoparticles that are suspended in them and have great heat conductivity. When mixed with regular coolants, these very small particles, which are between one and one hundred nanometers across, could make it much easier for heat to move through materials.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Improved Cooling through Greater Conductivity\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The research has focused on the use of nanofluids for vehicle cooling. It shows that base coolants, such as ethylene glycol, can significantly enhance thermal conductivity when mixed with nanoparticles, such as copper (Cu). A study found that compared to pure coolant, ethylene glycol with just 0.3% Cu nanoparticles increased heat conductivity by an impressive 45%.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"A real-life example of tiny heat exchangers that work better\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Nanofluids are better at moving heat, which can help cooling systems in vehicles. One such area is the creation of heat exchangers, which are necessary parts for moving heat from engine coolant to air outside the engine. Nanofluids could make it possible to make heat exchanges that are smaller and take up less space while still being able to cool things down. This could lead use of less fuel, lower material costs, and structures that are even simpler.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Nanofluids Keep The Engine Cool And Prevent Its Essential Parts\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In addition to engine cooling, the management of thermal load within automobiles is another potential application for nanofluids. Efficient heat dissipation is vital for the longevity and performance of modern cars, which primarily depend on electronic systems. Nanofluids can be a good option for cooling these delicate electronic components to avoid overheating and prolong their lifespan.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"A Novel Approach to Automotive Cooling in the Future\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Nanofluids have the potential to completely transform car cooling systems, but there are still a lot of obstacles to overcome. The automotive sector can benefit from the distinct characteristics of nanoparticles by integrating the knowledge of engineers, materials scientists, and environmental experts to develop next-gen cooling solutions that are efficient, dependable, and ecologically conscious.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"To Get The Most Out Of An Engine Needs Attention\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"To keep engine heat under control, you need to address more than one industry. Lubricant and coolant makers develop new fluids and additives, and engineers work hard to improve radiator placement and design. If we all work together, we can ensure that today’s engines run at their best swiftness. This will make them work better and last longer. If the automotive industry and the best automotive specialty makers work together, the engines that power our trips might be reliable and efficient.\"}]}]','2024-08-08 08:19:38.996000','2024-08-08 08:19:41.669000','2024-08-08 08:19:41.666000',2,2,'2024-07-22'),(9,'How Car Care Products Wow Buyers with Car Dealership Detailing','how-car-care-products-wow-buyers-with-car-dealership-detailing','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Remedy Management In The Automotive Industry\",\"italic\":true}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When a car is out for sale, it is important that the dealer handles the cleaning process correctly. This includes repairing the vehicle as quickly as possible and communicating with the customer about the process. The timing of the beautification and polishing of the vehicle and how the outcome is communicated can have a significant impact on the customer’s satisfaction.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Beyond Just A Pretty Finish With Car Care Products\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Customers want their cars to look amazing; that’s a given. But a savvy car dealer knows that a top-notch detailing job goes way beyond surface shine. It’s about customer experience, building trust, and even maximizing resale value.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"See, the car buying process can be stressful. Buyers worry about hidden problems, unexpected maintenance, and whether they’re truly getting a good deal. A thorough detailing job that is done right, can actually ease some of those anxieties of buyers.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"How Detailing Builds Confidence (and Sales)\",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Compare this with staging a house for sale. A thorough detail sends a message: “This car has been cared for.” It builds confidence in the buyer and makes them more likely to take the plunge. Plus, a sparkling clean car just flat out has a higher perceived value. That can make negotiations smoother and potentially even secure a better selling price.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It resonates with the Psychology of Shine, which says there’s something deeply satisfying about a perfectly clean, gleaming car—detailing taps into our desire for order and beauty, even extending to the idea of car care as self-care. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"But it’s not just about the final reveal. Here’s where car care product distributors can really make you shine:\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Transparency Builds Buyer Confidence\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Transparency-Builds-Buyer-Confidence.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Transparency-Builds-Buyer-Confidence.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Transparency_Builds_Buyer_Confidence_f1afe201c3.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Transparency-Builds-Buyer-Confidence.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Transparency_Builds_Buyer_Confidence_f1afe201c3\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":7.49,\"sizeInBytes\":7489,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Transparency_Builds_Buyer_Confidence_f1afe201c3.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Transparency-Builds-Buyer-Confidence.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Transparency_Builds_Buyer_Confidence_f1afe201c3\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":37.65,\"sizeInBytes\":37645,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Transparency_Builds_Buyer_Confidence_f1afe201c3.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Transparency-Builds-Buyer-Confidence.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Transparency_Builds_Buyer_Confidence_f1afe201c3\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":56.83,\"sizeInBytes\":56829,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Transparency_Builds_Buyer_Confidence_f1afe201c3.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Transparency-Builds-Buyer-Confidence.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Transparency_Builds_Buyer_Confidence_f1afe201c3\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":21.13,\"sizeInBytes\":21125,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Transparency_Builds_Buyer_Confidence_f1afe201c3.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Transparency_Builds_Buyer_Confidence_f1afe201c3\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":61.45,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-08T09:24:35.781Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-08T09:24:35.781Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Buying a used car can feel like rolling the dice. Smart dealers know the detailing process is an opportunity to build trust with potential buyers. If detailing turns up minor flaws (a stone chip, a small stain, a worn floor mat, swirl marks – tiny scratches in the paint, often caused by improper washing. Detailing products and techniques aim to remove or minimize these), don’t try to hide them!\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Instead, be proactive about disclosing these issues.  This kind of honesty signals the buyer that you’re not out to pull a fast one.  It also allows them to make informed decisions. Maybe they want that chip fixed before taking ownership, or perhaps it’s a factor in negotiating a better price.  Either way, transparency puts them in the driver’s seat and leads to a smoother transaction.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Time is of the Essence (For Dealers and Buyers!)\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Nobody likes to wait around, especially when they’re excited about a potential new car. Long detailing delays can sour a deal faster than you’d think. Make efficiency a priority in your detailing department. Invest in high-quality equipment, a streamlined workflow, and staff who know how to get the job done quickly without sacrificing quality.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"For pre-owned vehicles, a speedy turnaround is even more important.  It keeps the buyer engaged and shows you’re as excited as they are about getting that car ready for its new owner.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Wellness Angle: A Smart Selling Point\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"A detailed car does more than just look good – it can make buyers feel good.  A spotless, sanitized interior offers peace of mind, especially in a world where concerns about germs and cleanliness are commonplace.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Actively market your detailing process! Emphasize deep cleaning and sanitization techniques.  That “new car smell”?  It’s not just pleasant; it’s a signal that the car has been thoroughly prepared for a new owner.  These efforts can alleviate buyer concerns and become a strong selling point. Plus, detailing can help slow depreciation, the decline in a car’s value over time. A well-maintained car will retain its value better than one that has been neglected.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Right Tools for the Job\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"The-Right-Tools-for-the-Job.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"The-Right-Tools-for-the-Job.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/The_Right_Tools_for_the_Job_f9a6f80730.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_The-Right-Tools-for-the-Job.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_The_Right_Tools_for_the_Job_f9a6f80730\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":11.44,\"sizeInBytes\":11444,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_The_Right_Tools_for_the_Job_f9a6f80730.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_The-Right-Tools-for-the-Job.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_The_Right_Tools_for_the_Job_f9a6f80730\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":61.34,\"sizeInBytes\":61339,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_The_Right_Tools_for_the_Job_f9a6f80730.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_The-Right-Tools-for-the-Job.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_The_Right_Tools_for_the_Job_f9a6f80730\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":92.34,\"sizeInBytes\":92340,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_The_Right_Tools_for_the_Job_f9a6f80730.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_The-Right-Tools-for-the-Job.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_The_Right_Tools_for_the_Job_f9a6f80730\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":34.25,\"sizeInBytes\":34246,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_The_Right_Tools_for_the_Job_f9a6f80730.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"The_Right_Tools_for_the_Job_f9a6f80730\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":100.92,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-08T09:25:49.851Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-08T09:25:49.851Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Your dealership offers more than just cars—you offer an experience. For discerning buyers, premium detailing services can be the cherry on top. Here are some options you could offer:\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Ceramic coatings bond with the car’s paint, offering serious protection from scratches, fading, and grime. They also make the car insanely glossy. This is perfect for buyers who want long-lasting shine and easier maintenance.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"High-end polishes are perfect for the customer focused on removing fine scratches and swirls in their paint. Top-tier polishes deliver a flawless, mirror-like shine, ideal for restoring the luster of older vehicles or giving a brand-new car an extra wow factor.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Leather seats need special cleaners and conditioners. Stubborn stains require the right products. Offer these targeted services to buyers who care about keeping their car’s interior looking its best.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Going Green: Eco-Friendly Detailing\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In addition to these premium detailing services, it is also important to consider the environmental impact of your detailing business.\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Waterless Washes: Perfect for areas with water restrictions or for buyers concerned about water usage. These specialized formulas clean and protect without needing a hose.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Biodegradable Products: Show you care about the environment. Biodegradable cleaners are less harsh on the car and on waterways.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Minimal Packaging: Opting for larger refill containers instead of individual-use bottles reduces waste and shows your commitment to sustainability.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Car buyers are increasingly interested in sustainable practices, so eco-friendly detailing is a great way to appeal to this growing market segment and build a positive reputation for your dealership.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Importance of Expertise\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Even the best products won’t deliver maximum results without the right skills. Invest in training for your detailing staff! Make sure they know:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Product Knowledge: Why use a specific leather cleaner on that car versus a general interior cleaner on another? Your team should confidently explain the benefits of various products.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Proper Techniques: Applying a ceramic coating is way different than a basic wax. Improper use of detailing tools can actually damage the car. Train your team to achieve those pro-level results.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It’s in the Details: True pros know which areas to focus on and how to get that factory-fresh look. This kind of attention to detail is what truly impresses customers.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Detailing is too often seen as an unnecessary expense when, really, it’s a powerful tool for customer satisfaction and building a dealership’s reputation. And hey, we all love that feeling of driving away in a car that looks and feels brand new! and this can all happen with the help of car care products dealers in the UAE.\"}]}]','2024-08-08 09:31:51.046000','2024-08-08 09:31:55.343000','2024-08-08 09:31:55.336000',2,2,'2024-03-17'),(10,'Atlantic Lubricants – Give Power Performance To Your Cars and Exceed Expectations','atlantic-lubricants-give-power-performance-to-your-cars-and-exceed-expectations','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Your vehicle’s engine is a complex moving part. Pistons and gears spin, and metal constantly slides against metal.  Without the right shield, this creates friction.  Friction leads to heat, and heat wears down those precious parts faster than you’d think. Over time, performance tank breakdowns happen, and you’re facing costly repairs.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"That’s where lubrication makes all the difference.  A high-quality lubricant doesn’t just make things slippery. It forms a protective barrier, keeping metal surfaces from grinding against each other. This massively reduces wear and tear and even helps carry away excess heat. Just like fresh oil makes your car engine purr, specialized lubricants keep all kinds of machinery running smoothly.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Deciding on the wrong lubricant is like playing with fire. Different machines have unique needs based on how they’re designed and what they do. Some vehicle owners use a lubricant that’s too thin, gets gummy at the wrong temperature, or fails under pressure is a recipe for disaster. A company like Atlantic Lubricants takes the guesswork out of the equation. Their expertise and relentless testing ensure they have the perfect lubricant to protect your investments, whether you run a fleet of trucks or manage an entire factory.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"What Exactly is Atlantic Lubricants?\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic Lubricants is a well-known company specializing in powerful lubricants. They have a global reach, working with clients all over the world. The company boasts a top-notch facility and expert technicians to develop their advanced formulas. Their convenient distribution network guarantees easy access to their wide range of high-quality products.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Why OEM Approvals Are Key\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When buying lubricants, it’s essential to look for OEM approvals. OEM stands for Original Equipment Manufacturer. When an OEM approves a lubricant, it’s like they’re putting their stamp of approval on it. The OEM has thoroughly tested the lubricant with their own equipment, and it works perfectly!\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic Lubricants has earned plenty of OEM approvals. So, if you own expensive machinery with specific needs, there’s probably a perfect Atlantic lubricant for the job. They have options for cars, construction equipment, ships – virtually anything!\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Quality is in The Certification\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"OEM approvals aren’t the only proof of Atlantic’s top-tier quality. They also earn important certifications:\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ISO 9001-2015: This proves their manufacturing is always good; they focus on improvement, and customers come first.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ISO 17025-2015: This one is just for laboratory testing. It means you can depend on the analyses done during product development.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ISO 14001-2015: Being green matters! This certification shows Atlantic Lubricants cares about the environment.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"These world-class certifications tell you something critical – Atlantic Lubricants takes quality control incredibly seriously.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Finding Your Perfect Match - What They Offer\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Finding-Your-Perfect-Match-What-They-Offer.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Finding-Your-Perfect-Match-What-They-Offer.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Finding_Your_Perfect_Match_What_They_Offer_fedb56e18c.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Finding-Your-Perfect-Match-What-They-Offer.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Finding_Your_Perfect_Match_What_They_Offer_fedb56e18c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":10.85,\"sizeInBytes\":10845,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Finding_Your_Perfect_Match_What_They_Offer_fedb56e18c.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Finding-Your-Perfect-Match-What-They-Offer.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Finding_Your_Perfect_Match_What_They_Offer_fedb56e18c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":100.25,\"sizeInBytes\":100245,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Finding_Your_Perfect_Match_What_They_Offer_fedb56e18c.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Finding-Your-Perfect-Match-What-They-Offer.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Finding_Your_Perfect_Match_What_They_Offer_fedb56e18c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":35.38,\"sizeInBytes\":35383,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Finding_Your_Perfect_Match_What_They_Offer_fedb56e18c.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Finding-Your-Perfect-Match-What-They-Offer.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Finding_Your_Perfect_Match_What_They_Offer_fedb56e18c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":65.85,\"sizeInBytes\":65854,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Finding_Your_Perfect_Match_What_They_Offer_fedb56e18c.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Finding_Your_Perfect_Match_What_They_Offer_fedb56e18c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":109.63,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-08T09:48:50.652Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-08T09:48:50.652Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic Lubricants has the right lubricant for almost any job. Here’s just a sample of what they offer:\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Automotive Lubricants:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Oils and fluids to protect engines, transmissions, brakes, and more. Works with cars, trucks, and heavy machinery.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Get maximum protection in sub-zero temperatures with Atlantic Super Synthech SAE 0W40 API SN. Its super-thin formula flows smoothly from the moment you turn the key. it reduces engine wear during those critical first seconds, and this is ideal for high-performance cars that need premium cold-weather performance and outstanding durability.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC FULLY SYNTHETIC NEOTERIC ULTRA 10W40 SP\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The ultimate choice for modern engines requiring superior protection with an emphasis on fuel efficiency. Atlantic Fully Synthetic Neoteric Ultra 10W40 SP helps maximize your engine’s potential with extended drain intervals and cutting-edge automotive lubricantsfor long-term reliability.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC SYNTHECH ULTRA SUPER MOTOR OIL SAE 5W-30 API SL\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Designed for every day and high-mileage vehicles, Atlantic Synthech Ultra Super Motor Oil SAE 5W-30 API SL delivers dependable protection year-round. Engineered to prevent sludge build-up, boost fuel efficiency, and maximize engine lifespan.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC SYNTHECH ULTRA SUPER MOTOR OIL SAE 5W-40 API SN/CF\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When your engine faces tough conditions, Atlantic Synthech Ultra Super Motor Oil SAE 5W-40 API SN/CF rises to the challenge. Perfect for performance cars and diesel engines, its formula fights oil breakdown under high temperatures and provides superior wear protection.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC ULTRA SUPER SYNTHETIC ENGINE OIL SAE 5W-40 API SP\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Maximize your engine’s longevity with Atlantic Ultra Super Synthetic Engine Oil SAE 5W-40 API SP. Specially formulated for modern, high-output engines, it offers incredible cleanliness and outstanding performance in extreme conditions. Protects critical components while maximizing engine efficiency.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Industrial Lubricants:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"industrial-lubricants.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"industrial-lubricants.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/industrial_lubricants_acb4cd4ca7.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_industrial-lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_industrial_lubricants_acb4cd4ca7\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":10.21,\"sizeInBytes\":10207,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_industrial_lubricants_acb4cd4ca7.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_industrial-lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_industrial_lubricants_acb4cd4ca7\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":34.68,\"sizeInBytes\":34683,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_industrial_lubricants_acb4cd4ca7.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_industrial-lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_industrial_lubricants_acb4cd4ca7\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":66.43,\"sizeInBytes\":66432,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_industrial_lubricants_acb4cd4ca7.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_industrial-lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_industrial_lubricants_acb4cd4ca7\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":103.27,\"sizeInBytes\":103267,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_industrial_lubricants_acb4cd4ca7.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"industrial_lubricants_acb4cd4ca7\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":113.64,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-08T09:52:54.532Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-08T09:52:54.532Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Maintain peak performance of your machines with an array of industrial lubricants suitable for hydraulic systems, bearings, gears, turbines, and much more. Atlantic Lubricants’ range is geared towards diverse sectors like manufacturing, construction, mining, and power generation.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC STEAM CYLINDER OIL – Gear and Cylinder\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Keep your steam engines and heavy machinery running smoothly with the ATLANTIC STEAM CYLINDER OIL. It’s designed to withstand the intense heat and pressure of steam systems. This lubricant reduces friction, protects cylinders, and helps your equipment last longer, even under demanding conditions.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC REFRIGERATION COMPRESSOR OIL\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC REFRIGERATION COMPRESSOR OIL is your go-to for efficient and reliable refrigeration systems. Its specialized formula maintains optimal flow in cold temperatures. It effectively combats wear and tear in compressors, preventing costly breakdowns and keeping your equipment working.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC HEAT TRANSFER FLUIDS\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Designed for precise temperature control, ATLANTIC HEAT TRANSFER FLUIDS excel in a variety of industrial applications. These fluids efficiently move heat away from critical components, maintaining optimal operating temperatures. Their stability ensures long-lasting performance and dependable heat transfer.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC GEAR EP – Extreme Pressure Oil\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When your gears face heavy loads and extreme pressure, ATLANTIC GEAR EP delivers. This premium lubricant creates a tough protective film between gear teeth, preventing wear and tear. It’s an excellent choice for industrial gearboxes and other equipment working under challenging conditions.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Marine Lubricants:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Marine-Lubricants.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Marine-Lubricants.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Marine_Lubricants_af7652989f.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Marine-Lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Marine_Lubricants_af7652989f\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":8.45,\"sizeInBytes\":8451,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Marine_Lubricants_af7652989f.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Marine-Lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Marine_Lubricants_af7652989f\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":56.52,\"sizeInBytes\":56520,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Marine_Lubricants_af7652989f.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Marine-Lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Marine_Lubricants_af7652989f\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":29.06,\"sizeInBytes\":29062,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Marine_Lubricants_af7652989f.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Marine-Lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Marine_Lubricants_af7652989f\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":89.03,\"sizeInBytes\":89026,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Marine_Lubricants_af7652989f.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Marine_Lubricants_af7652989f\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":97.2,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-08T10:25:20.101Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-08T10:25:20.101Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Tough oils and greases specially made for ocean-going equipment. It protects engines and extends their lifespan despite the harsh saltwater environment.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC TRUNK PISTON ENGINE OIL\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Protect large, hardworking marine diesel engines with ATLANTIC TRUNK PISTON ENGINE OIL. It handles these engines’ intense conditions, preventing harmful deposits and neutralizing corrosive acids. The result? A cleaner engine, improved efficiency, and long-term reliability on the open water.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC PREMIUM PLUS 2-CYCLE OUTBOARD – 2-Stroke Engine Oil\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Power your water adventures with ATLANTIC PREMIUM PLUS 2-CYCLE OUTBOARD. This specialized 2-stroke oil burns clean to limit emissions. It offers excellent lubrication under the rigors of marine use, maximizing your outboard motor’s lifespan and ensuring it runs at its best.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC OUTBOARD OIL 4T\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Give your 4-stroke outboard the attention it deserves with ATLANTIC OUTBOARD OIL 4T. Tailor-made for this type of engine, this oil boasts a robust additive package. It keeps your engine clean, minimizes wear, and optimizes performance for peak enjoyment on the water.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC MARINOL GEN 4\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC MARINOL GEN 4 is the next generation of marine diesel engine oils. Its advanced formula goes beyond ordinary requirements, delivering exceptional deposit control. It offers outstanding performance even in the toughest marine environments, guaranteeing peace of mind on the open seas.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Car Care Products: If you’re a car buff, check out these solutions! The Atlantic has cleaners, waxes, shampoos, and everything else you need to make your ride look its best.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Why Pick Atlantic Lubricants?\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Why-Pick-Atlantic-Lubricants.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Why-Pick-Atlantic-Lubricants.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Why_Pick_Atlantic_Lubricants_5330ea92a2.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Why-Pick-Atlantic-Lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Why_Pick_Atlantic_Lubricants_5330ea92a2\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":9.54,\"sizeInBytes\":9537,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Why_Pick_Atlantic_Lubricants_5330ea92a2.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Why-Pick-Atlantic-Lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Why_Pick_Atlantic_Lubricants_5330ea92a2\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":53.02,\"sizeInBytes\":53020,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Why_Pick_Atlantic_Lubricants_5330ea92a2.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Why-Pick-Atlantic-Lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Why_Pick_Atlantic_Lubricants_5330ea92a2\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":81.42,\"sizeInBytes\":81418,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Why_Pick_Atlantic_Lubricants_5330ea92a2.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Why-Pick-Atlantic-Lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Why_Pick_Atlantic_Lubricants_5330ea92a2\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":29.02,\"sizeInBytes\":29015,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Why_Pick_Atlantic_Lubricants_5330ea92a2.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Why_Pick_Atlantic_Lubricants_5330ea92a2\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":87.46,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-08T10:23:36.074Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-08T10:23:36.074Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Why Atlantic Grease and Lubricants Focuses on Advanced Formulas\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Think about how much car engines have changed in recent years. They’re smaller, more complex, and squeeze out way more power per liter than ever before. Carmakers put incredible demands on them, and every component – even the engine oil – needs to be up to task. That’s why there’s been a big push towards synthetic oils. This advanced type of lubricant delivers consistent performance with less risk of breaking down at extreme temperatures.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Here at Atlantic Grease and Lubricants, we never stop chasing perfection. We don’t just meet industry standards; we want to leave them in the dust. This dedication led us to develop our groundbreaking PureSynth Technology.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"PureSynth Technology: Protection Without Compromise\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The “base oil” in a lubricant makes up most of its volume and sets the stage for everything else. Our PureSynth Technology creates base oils with incredibly pure and strong molecular bonds. Traditional oils start with crude oil, a complex mixture that takes lots of refining to reach the desired standards. That’s one reason why traditional oils leave more room for impurities and inconsistencies.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"PureSynth Technology makes the core of our top-tier products like Atlantic UltraTech. This line of engine oils boasts 99.5% purity, delivering unparalleled protection for today’s hardest-working engines. Deposits that rob performance? Virtually eliminated. Harmful wear and tear? Significantly reduced. And those cold starts where conventional oil feels like molasses? Atlantic UltraTech flows freely for instant lubrication, no matter the season.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Active Cleansing Technology- Next-Level Cleanliness\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"At Atlantic, we know an exceptional base oil is just the start. That’s why we pair PureSynth Technology with our proprietary Active Cleansing Technology to create products like Atlantic UltraTech Plus. This potent cleansing formula works aggressively to flush out harmful sludge and prevent corrosive contaminant build-up. What you get is an engine that stays virtually factory-clean, ready to deliver optimal performance at any moment.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Atlantic Performance Advantage\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When you use Atlantic lubricants and greases for your car, you’re not just protecting your engine – you’re unlocking its full potential. Here’s what you can expect:\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Longer Engine Life: Internal components operate in ideal conditions, significantly extending the overall lifespan of your engine.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Reduced Maintenance Bills: Better protection means fewer unexpected issues and more worry-free miles.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Fuel Economy Boost: A cleaner, more efficient engine makes the most of every drop of fuel you pay for.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Smoother, Quieter Operation: Our advanced formulas minimize friction for a satisfyingly smooth and silent driving experience.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Whether you’re driving a daily commuter, a high-performance machine, or a heavy-duty workhorse, Atlantic Grease, and Lubricants has the perfect formula to exceed your expectations. We aren’t just focused on the present – we’re constantly researching and innovating to deliver the lubrication solutions of the future.\"}]}]','2024-08-08 10:27:44.252000','2024-08-08 10:27:46.822000','2024-08-08 10:27:46.815000',2,2,'2024-03-11'),(11,'Grease vs. Lubricant: The Right Lubrication for Different Works','grease-vs-lubricant-the-right-lubrication-for-different-works','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"If you are a vehicle owner or are related to an industrial environment, choosing the right lubricant is necessary for the unbreakable working of the machinery/engine and its related tools. Grease and oil have distinct strengths, and to understand those differences is your first step toward smoother operations. This is also necessary for higher efficiency and healthier machines. \"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"What is Grease, and Why Would You Choose It?\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Grease functions in the same way as oil, much like the sort of oil that you put in your automobile. On the other hand, thickening is caused by a chemical that gives the grease its semi-solid consistency. Consider the thickening to be a sponge that is responsible for retaining greases in place.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Giving power is the most significant benefit that grease possesses. Grease, in contrast to oil, which will eventually leak away, will remain in place in essential components such as bearings, gears, and chains. This substance forms a barrier that is both protective and long-lasting, and it sticks to metal surfaces.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Contamination Fighter: Grease performs the function of a sealant, preventing dust, water, and other impurities from entering the system, which can lead to wear and tear on the equipment.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"NLGI Grades: You’ve probably seen these numbers on grease containers. That’s the National Lubrication Grease Institute (NLGI) grade, which tells you how soft or stiff the grease is. Higher numbers refer to thicker, stiffer greases.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When Oil is the Better Bet\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Flow is Key: Some scenarios call for a lubricant that reaches hidden spots or nooks and crannies. Oil flows freely. It reaches those areas where grease might not be reached. That’s why you’ll often find oil in circulating systems, gearboxes, and even inside your car’s engine.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Heat Dissipation: Oil takes the win when it comes to cooling capabilities. Some specialized oils can even actively transfer heat away from hot components. It helps protect your equipment.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Easier Clean-Out: When frequent flushing and lubricant replenishment are needed, oil is simpler to replace entirely than grease.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Greasing vs. Oiling: Real-World Applications\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Leakage: If preventing leaks is a major concern, grease will win hands-down. It creates a more effective seal.\"}]},{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Exposure: Open gears or other components under constant assault from contaminants are better protected by a thick layer of grease.\"}]},{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\rFrequency: When constantly reapplying lubricant isn’t practical, grease gives you longer lubrication intervals, reducing maintenance time and costs.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Myth busting  and Next Steps\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Fact or Fiction? Greasing more often always means better protection.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Often, this is FALSE. Excessive lubrication can cause its own problems – forcing out seals, attracting grime, or even generating increased heat that breaks down the grease faster.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The topic goes surprisingly deep! Beyond NLGI Grades: \"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"What Else Your Grease Label Should Tell You\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Tackling Contamination: Which Grease Thickeners Stand Up Best?\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Is Your Industry Wasting Money on The Wrong Lubricants?\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Need Help Now? Choose Wisely When Faced with Real Issues\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Equipment Down? Is leaking of Lubricant the culprit? If so, the solution could be as simple as switching to a thicker grease, designed to stay in place.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Are you Struggling with frequent breakdowns in a harsh environment? Investigate different greases formulated to repel harmful contaminants or handle extreme temperatures.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Unsure? Don’t make critical lubrication decisions based on guesses! A consultation with a lubrication expert can provide personalized guidance to optimize reliability and lower costs.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Supply chain Snags? Here’s How to Choose a Substitute Grease (Without Risking Damage)\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Supply-chain-Snags-Heres-How-to-Choose-a-Substitute-Grease-Without-Risking-Damage.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Supply-chain-Snags-Heres-How-to-Choose-a-Substitute-Grease-Without-Risking-Damage.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Supply_chain_Snags_Heres_How_to_Choose_a_Substitute_Grease_Without_Risking_Damage_3cc07a8af9.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Supply-chain-Snags-Heres-How-to-Choose-a-Substitute-Grease-Without-Risking-Damage.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Supply_chain_Snags_Heres_How_to_Choose_a_Substitute_Grease_Without_Risking_Damage_3cc07a8af9\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":10.44,\"sizeInBytes\":10435,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Supply_chain_Snags_Heres_How_to_Choose_a_Substitute_Grease_Without_Risking_Damage_3cc07a8af9.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Supply-chain-Snags-Heres-How-to-Choose-a-Substitute-Grease-Without-Risking-Damage.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Supply_chain_Snags_Heres_How_to_Choose_a_Substitute_Grease_Without_Risking_Damage_3cc07a8af9\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":33.67,\"sizeInBytes\":33673,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Supply_chain_Snags_Heres_How_to_Choose_a_Substitute_Grease_Without_Risking_Damage_3cc07a8af9.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Supply-chain-Snags-Heres-How-to-Choose-a-Substitute-Grease-Without-Risking-Damage.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Supply_chain_Snags_Heres_How_to_Choose_a_Substitute_Grease_Without_Risking_Damage_3cc07a8af9\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":62.85,\"sizeInBytes\":62848,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Supply_chain_Snags_Heres_How_to_Choose_a_Substitute_Grease_Without_Risking_Damage_3cc07a8af9.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Supply-chain-Snags-Heres-How-to-Choose-a-Substitute-Grease-Without-Risking-Damage.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Supply_chain_Snags_Heres_How_to_Choose_a_Substitute_Grease_Without_Risking_Damage_3cc07a8af9\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":96.92,\"sizeInBytes\":96920,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Supply_chain_Snags_Heres_How_to_Choose_a_Substitute_Grease_Without_Risking_Damage_3cc07a8af9.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Supply_chain_Snags_Heres_How_to_Choose_a_Substitute_Grease_Without_Risking_Damage_3cc07a8af9\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":105.45,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-08T10:55:06.665Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-08T10:55:06.665Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let’s be real – lubricants and grease supply chain disruptions have thrown a wrench on even the best-laid maintenance plans. If your go-to grease is out of stock and equipment needs lubrication, it’s understandable to feel desperate. But don’t panic and resist the urge to grab just “anything thick” off the shelf. Here’s a plan to navigate substitute grease choices safely:\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Compatibility Check: Mixing Greases Can Be a Recipe for Disaster\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Thickener types are like the different flours used in baking. Some can blend, but others will form a clumpy, unworkable mess. The same goes for combining greases with the wrong thickener type! At best, you get poor performance, but at worst, it can ruin your equipment.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Here’s your quick reference guide:\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Generally Compatible:\",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Lithium + Lithium\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Calcium + Calcium\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Polyurea + Polyurea (in most cases)\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Beware Mixing:\",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Simple vs. Complex Soaps (Lithium and Calcium fall into different soap categories)\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Clay-based thickeners\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"NEVER MIX:\",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Aluminum Complex on its own – it’s the odd one out!\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Match Essential Traits, Don’t Settle for Less\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Finding grease, you can get is tempting, but if it isn’t right for your equipment, it’s a liability, not a solution. When looking at substitutes, focus on these points:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"NLGI Grade: Ideally, match the same grade or go only one step thicker. It is too drastic a change, and you risk seals blowing out or excessive drag.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Operating Temperature: Know the highs and lows your equipment typically experiences. Match (or even better, exceed) the temperature range the substitute grease is designed for.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Special Needs: Water resistance, extreme pressure additives, compatibility with food-grade processes, etc. Don’t sacrifice needs that protect your machinery or your business!\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Temporary Fix or Is It Time to Switch?\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"What is the likelihood that this condition of being out of stock will be a short-term or a long-term reality? Take into consideration this:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Short-Term Struggle: You should go with a readily accessible alternative that is as close as feasible to the original, and you should make arrangements to go back to the original as soon as the supply returns to normal.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Long-term Shift: Take advantage of this chance to find a grease that outperforms the one you initially selected or that offers new benefits such as longer intervals between relubrication. It is possible that this disturbance will turn out to be a Godsend!\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Take Special Assistance!\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When you are faced with challenging choices regarding the replacement of grease, do not be afraid to obtain the assistance of a lubrication specialist.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"They understand the complex details that may not be readily apparent to you. If you want to involve an expert early on it can prevent costly equipment damage and minimize risks.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Need help determining a safe substitute or want to find out if now is the perfect time to discover a better fit for your plant’s lubricants? Contact us for a consultation!\",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Beyond “One Size Fits All”: Selecting Lubricants for Industrial Needs\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Beyond-One-Size-Fits-All-Selecting-Lubricants-for-Industrial-Needs.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Beyond-One-Size-Fits-All-Selecting-Lubricants-for-Industrial-Needs.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Beyond_One_Size_Fits_All_Selecting_Lubricants_for_Industrial_Needs_505cb1c91d.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Beyond-One-Size-Fits-All-Selecting-Lubricants-for-Industrial-Needs.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Beyond_One_Size_Fits_All_Selecting_Lubricants_for_Industrial_Needs_505cb1c91d\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":9.22,\"sizeInBytes\":9222,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Beyond_One_Size_Fits_All_Selecting_Lubricants_for_Industrial_Needs_505cb1c91d.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Beyond-One-Size-Fits-All-Selecting-Lubricants-for-Industrial-Needs.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Beyond_One_Size_Fits_All_Selecting_Lubricants_for_Industrial_Needs_505cb1c91d\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":56.61,\"sizeInBytes\":56608,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Beyond_One_Size_Fits_All_Selecting_Lubricants_for_Industrial_Needs_505cb1c91d.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Beyond-One-Size-Fits-All-Selecting-Lubricants-for-Industrial-Needs.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Beyond_One_Size_Fits_All_Selecting_Lubricants_for_Industrial_Needs_505cb1c91d\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":29.89,\"sizeInBytes\":29890,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Beyond_One_Size_Fits_All_Selecting_Lubricants_for_Industrial_Needs_505cb1c91d.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Beyond-One-Size-Fits-All-Selecting-Lubricants-for-Industrial-Needs.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Beyond_One_Size_Fits_All_Selecting_Lubricants_for_Industrial_Needs_505cb1c91d\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":87.96,\"sizeInBytes\":87962,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Beyond_One_Size_Fits_All_Selecting_Lubricants_for_Industrial_Needs_505cb1c91d.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Beyond_One_Size_Fits_All_Selecting_Lubricants_for_Industrial_Needs_505cb1c91d\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":96.27,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-08T10:56:17.628Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-08T10:56:17.628Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Not all industries are the same and neither are their needs for machine lubrication. The specialized lubricant categories are key to smoother operations to protect your expensive equipment, and it is necessary to understand.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When Your Industry Goes Beyond the Basics\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Here’s why thinking beyond your typical oil or grease choices might be necessary:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Food Processing: Contamination here isn’t just a matter of machinery breakdown, it’s a major safety concern. That’s where NSF-certified food-grade lubricants come into play. Accidental contact won’t taint your products.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Extremes of Temperature: Many lubricants become unpredictable under searing heat or bitter cold. High-temp lubricants with tailored formulas stay viscous at temperatures that turn standard grease gummy. Think steel mills, bakeries, etc. Low-temp lubricants prevent turning solid and seizing critical parts, for applications like free storage operations.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Environmental Impact: In areas with environmental sensitivities or where machinery must withstand the elements, biodegradable lubricants offer protection without long-term environmental harm if there’s accidental leakage. This isn’t just feel-good – regulations sometimes mandate the use of specific lubricant types!\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Deciphering the Label: How to Make Sense of All Those Technical Specs\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Lubricants aren’t just labeled “grease” or “motor oil.” Understanding those key specs helps ensure you’re getting what you need:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"NSF Certifications: Look for H1 certifications (incidental food contact possible), or more restrictive standards like H2 or H3 if needed.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Viscosity and NLGI: Remember, these dictate how thick the lubricant is. Match your operation’s needs.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Base Oil: Mineral oils are common, but synthetics are often engineered for extreme environments or longer service life.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Additives: Look for corrosion inhibitors in wet environments, extreme pressure (EP) additives for heavily loaded parts, etc.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The True Cost of “Good-Enough” Lubrication\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"The-True-Cost-of-Good-Enough-Lubrication.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"The-True-Cost-of-Good-Enough-Lubrication.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/The_True_Cost_of_Good_Enough_Lubrication_3c6ec473b3.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_The-True-Cost-of-Good-Enough-Lubrication.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_The_True_Cost_of_Good_Enough_Lubrication_3c6ec473b3\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":10.42,\"sizeInBytes\":10419,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_The_True_Cost_of_Good_Enough_Lubrication_3c6ec473b3.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_The-True-Cost-of-Good-Enough-Lubrication.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_The_True_Cost_of_Good_Enough_Lubrication_3c6ec473b3\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":56.86,\"sizeInBytes\":56862,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_The_True_Cost_of_Good_Enough_Lubrication_3c6ec473b3.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_The-True-Cost-of-Good-Enough-Lubrication.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_The_True_Cost_of_Good_Enough_Lubrication_3c6ec473b3\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":85.96,\"sizeInBytes\":85956,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_The_True_Cost_of_Good_Enough_Lubrication_3c6ec473b3.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_The-True-Cost-of-Good-Enough-Lubrication.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_The_True_Cost_of_Good_Enough_Lubrication_3c6ec473b3\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":31.69,\"sizeInBytes\":31690,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_The_True_Cost_of_Good_Enough_Lubrication_3c6ec473b3.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"The_True_Cost_of_Good_Enough_Lubrication_3c6ec473b3\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":93.21,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-08T10:57:58.663Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-08T10:57:58.663Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“All-purpose” might seem affordable, but in the wrong circumstances, it’s actually the most expensive choice! Here’s the breakdown:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Equipment Breakdown: Lubricants not up to the task accelerate wear and tear, leading to premature component failures and costly repairs.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Unexpected Downtime: Having a production line crippled because lubrication wasn’t a priority loses the business money far beyond the price difference in buying suitable atlantic lubricants.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Safety/Regulatory Concerns: In food processing, using the wrong lubricant can result in recalls, lost business, and severe regulatory penalties.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Environmental Harm: In sensitive areas, a simple leak from an ill-suited lubricant can mean costly environmental remediation, not to mention damage to your business’s reputation.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Not Sure Where to Start? Experts Guide the Way\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It’s OKAY not to be an expert on every variety of lubrication out there. Seeking the advice of a specialist often pays for itself in reliability and optimized maintenance costs. Contact us if you’re unsure what lubricants best suit your unique operating conditions!\"}]}]','2024-08-08 11:01:21.441000','2024-08-08 11:01:28.376000','2024-08-08 11:01:28.368000',2,2,'2024-03-30'),(12,'Get The Most Out Of Your Equipment With The Power Of The Best Grease','get-the-most-out-of-your-equipment-with-the-power-of-the-best-grease','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"For centuries, people have used lubricants to make machinery run smoothly. Early greases were simple mixtures of animal fats or plant-based oils. The discovery of petroleum and advances in chemistry revolutionized greases. It gave us the high-performance lubricants we rely on today. Modern greases are complex blends of base oils, thickeners, and specialized additives designed to withstand extreme temperatures, heavy loads, and harsh environments. The selection of the right grease is crucial – it protects your equipment, helps it run better, and saves you money in the long run.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Grease Selection: A Strategic Choice\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The decision on the proper grease isn’t about just grabbing any old tub. It’s about understanding what that grease will face in the real world – the pressure, the heat, the constant struggle. Making the wrong choice will harm the machine and result in giving up too soon. A poorly chosen grease is more likely to lead to inefficient operation and premature wear rather than immediate damage. Believe it or not, grease makers have been puzzling over this for a long time. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Back in 1952, one article put it like this: “We need grease that’s strong, won’t melt, but still flows where it needs to. Oh, and it can’t make your machine work any harder than it has to!” \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"While the technology has changed, the core challenges remain. The selection of the right grease means understanding the specific needs of your machinery and how different greases respond to those conditions.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It turns out that the direction is still true. Every good grease needs to be checked in a different machine to keep your equipment humming along. While thorough testing is essential, initial lab tests (like penetrometer readings or dropping points) can reveal a lot about grease properties before field trials.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Consistency For Optimal Performance\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Consistency-For-Optimal-Performance.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Consistency-For-Optimal-Performance.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Consistency_For_Optimal_Performance_0099d2c3b9.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Consistency-For-Optimal-Performance.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Consistency_For_Optimal_Performance_0099d2c3b9\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":9.64,\"sizeInBytes\":9644,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Consistency_For_Optimal_Performance_0099d2c3b9.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Consistency-For-Optimal-Performance.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Consistency_For_Optimal_Performance_0099d2c3b9\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":52.04,\"sizeInBytes\":52039,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Consistency_For_Optimal_Performance_0099d2c3b9.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Consistency-For-Optimal-Performance.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Consistency_For_Optimal_Performance_0099d2c3b9\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":77.33,\"sizeInBytes\":77327,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Consistency_For_Optimal_Performance_0099d2c3b9.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Consistency-For-Optimal-Performance.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Consistency_For_Optimal_Performance_0099d2c3b9\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":28.84,\"sizeInBytes\":28839,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Consistency_For_Optimal_Performance_0099d2c3b9.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Consistency_For_Optimal_Performance_0099d2c3b9\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":84.01,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-09T05:34:30.600Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-09T05:34:30.600Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The research has a fascinating take on grease. It says that even with all the modern advancements, making the perfect grease is still a tricky business. Why? Because so many tiny things can change the final product – using the machines, the exact process. It affects even how experienced the grease maker is!\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"What makes grease unique? It has a special property called rheology. Another scientist breaks down a key concept about grease rheology. Most things are either solid (they hold their shape) or liquid (they flow easily). Grease is a bit of both! That’s why it seems thick when it’s just sitting there but thins out and gets to work when your machine starts moving. Scientists call that “shear thinning.”\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Base Oil Controls Key Properties\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The base oil is the heart of grease! Here’s why it plays such a critical role:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Base oil is the Main Ingredient: Best grease lubricant might seem super thick, but they’re mostly made of base oil (think around 70-90%). The rest is the thickener and the additives. It Determines Key Properties:\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Viscosity: How thick or thin the grease flows is primarily controlled by the base oil. Viscosity, along with the type and amount of thickener used. This is essential for matching machinery needs – fast-moving parts need thinner grease, while slow, heavy-duty parts need thicker protection.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Temperature Tolerance: The base oil determines how well the grease handles heat and cold. Some base oils stay stable in extreme temperatures, perfect for harsh operating conditions. This is important for matching the conditions your machine operates in.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It provides lubrication: While the grease looks thick, it actually ‘thins out’ when the machine gets going. The lubrication action comes directly from the base oil that is flowing between the moving parts.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Think of it like making soup:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Base Oil = The Broth: It’s the foundation, and its flavor and consistency influence the whole dish.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Thickener = Flour or Starch: It helps create that thicker texture but doesn’t provide the main lubrication.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Additives = The Spices: Fine-tune the final product, but without the broth, you wouldn’t have soup at all!\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Thickener: Grease’s Special Ingredient\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"The-Thickener-Grease-Special-Ingredient.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"The-Thickener-Grease-Special-Ingredient.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/The_Thickener_Grease_Special_Ingredient_bde75df047.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_The-Thickener-Grease-Special-Ingredient.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_The_Thickener_Grease_Special_Ingredient_bde75df047\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":6.62,\"sizeInBytes\":6619,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_The_Thickener_Grease_Special_Ingredient_bde75df047.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_The-Thickener-Grease-Special-Ingredient.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_The_Thickener_Grease_Special_Ingredient_bde75df047\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":57.91,\"sizeInBytes\":57912,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_The_Thickener_Grease_Special_Ingredient_bde75df047.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_The-Thickener-Grease-Special-Ingredient.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_The_Thickener_Grease_Special_Ingredient_bde75df047\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":20.12,\"sizeInBytes\":20120,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_The_Thickener_Grease_Special_Ingredient_bde75df047.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_The-Thickener-Grease-Special-Ingredient.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_The_Thickener_Grease_Special_Ingredient_bde75df047\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":38.15,\"sizeInBytes\":38146,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_The_Thickener_Grease_Special_Ingredient_bde75df047.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"The_Thickener_Grease_Special_Ingredient_bde75df047\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":62.82,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-09T05:35:41.275Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-09T05:35:41.275Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"What gives grease its unique texture? It’s the thickener! It’s the thickener! This is a special ingredient that turns plain Oil into something thicker and stickier. Thickeners can be all sorts of things – soap, certain types of clay, or other specialized compounds. They look different under a microscope – some are like fibers, some like little balls, and others like flat plates. The shape and type of thickener you choose changes your grease, making it:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Handle heat better (or worse)\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Stay put in wet conditions!\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Be softer or stiffer, depending on what your machine needs.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Complex Greases Offer Enhanced Protection\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The thickener isn’t just about making grease thick – it has a huge impact on how your grease behaves in the real world. Think about how different it feels to spread peanut butter versus jelly. That difference is largely due to the thickener! Here’s how it impacts your grease:\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Appearance And Texture: \"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The type of thickener influences whether your grease is buttery smooth, a bit stringy, or even slightly grainy feel. This matters because it affects how the grease sticks to parts and whether it will stay where you put it.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Melting Point: \"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"This is crucial! The ‘dropping point’ is the temperature where your grease gets too hot, turns into a runny liquid, and stops protecting your machinery. Different thickeners handle heat differently.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Staying Power: \"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Some thickeners hold up better to the constant rubbing and pressure inside a working machine. A grease with a weak thickener will break down too fast and need to be replaced more often.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Water Resistance: \"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Does your machinery get exposed to moisture? Some thickeners wash away easily, while others are designed to cling to metal even in wet environments.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Pumping Power: \"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"If your grease needs to be moved through tubes or hoses, the thickener matters. Certain types of grease are easier to pump than others, which is important for proper lubrication.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"There are simple greases, and then there are complex thickener greases. These are made with extra ingredients that boost its performance, usually letting it handle higher temperatures before it gives out.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Manufacturers point out that making these thickeners is a delicate process. It is like a science experiment – a little too much heat or not stirring it long enough, and you could end up with a totally different result!\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Thickener Properties Affect Grease Performance\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The classic greases you probably think of usually use thickeners made from things like lithium, calcium, or a few other metals. The most popular worldwide is lithium grease. The funny thing is the choice of metal matters a lot! It changes how well the grease handles heat, whether it gets affected by water or other important stuff. Kumar points out that some thickeners, like those specialized calcium sulfonate ones, are naturally better at handling wet conditions than others. Greases made with clay are interesting – they don’t melt at a single point, so they get used in really hot machines.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"One of the grease experts emphasizes that the thickener is probably the most important ingredient. It sets the stage for what that grease can do. Is it meant for extreme heat, around water, or maybe even in machines that handle food? (Hint: lithium is a no-go for food-grade grease). The cool thing is that some thickeners are so good on their own that you don’t need to add as many extra chemicals to get the performance you need.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Additives Are The Superpowers\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Additives-Are-The-Superpowers.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Additives-Are-The-Superpowers.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Additives_Are_The_Superpowers_10abd5e153.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Additives-Are-The-Superpowers.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Additives_Are_The_Superpowers_10abd5e153\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":6.71,\"sizeInBytes\":6714,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Additives_Are_The_Superpowers_10abd5e153.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Additives-Are-The-Superpowers.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Additives_Are_The_Superpowers_10abd5e153\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":37.54,\"sizeInBytes\":37538,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Additives_Are_The_Superpowers_10abd5e153.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Additives-Are-The-Superpowers.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Additives_Are_The_Superpowers_10abd5e153\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":20.29,\"sizeInBytes\":20294,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Additives_Are_The_Superpowers_10abd5e153.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Additives-Are-The-Superpowers.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Additives_Are_The_Superpowers_10abd5e153\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":56.37,\"sizeInBytes\":56366,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Additives_Are_The_Superpowers_10abd5e153.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Additives_Are_The_Superpowers_10abd5e153\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":61.07,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-09T05:37:12.316Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-09T05:37:12.316Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"We already know the base oil is the foundation of grease, and the thickener gives it texture. But there’s a third key ingredient – additives! For example, additives can prevent rust, reduce wear under heavy loads, or enhance a grease’s ability to cling to metal in wet environments. These are the special chemicals that work like performance boosters, giving grease abilities it wouldn’t naturally have. \"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Why Additives Matter\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Machines work in all kinds of tough conditions. Extreme temperatures, moisture, and heavy loads – can all push grease beyond its limits. Additives help it to survive those challenges! They fine-tune the grease and make it stronger, longer lasting, and more adaptable.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Temperature Tamers\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"One common type of additive is called a viscosity modifier. These clever chemicals help the grease handle big temperature swings. They make sure the grease doesn’t get too thick in the cold or too thin in the heat. This means your machinery has consistent lubrication, whether you’re working in summer or winter temperatures.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"How Manufacturing Impacts Grease Performance\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The way grease is made has a big impact on how it performs. Choosing the right process ensures your grease can handle whatever you throw at it. Here’s a look at common methods:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Open Kettle: This classic method is good for large batches and works with a variety of grease types.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Closed Kettle: Uses high heat and pressure – perfect for greases that need those conditions to form correctly.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Hybrid Approach: Sometimes, factories combine methods. They might start the process in a closed system for special chemistry, then finish things off in an open kettle.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Right Method Means The Right Results\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Manufacturing method directly impacts important grease properties:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Shear Stability: How well does the grease hold up under stress? The process used plays a role. This matters for high-speed or heavy-duty applications.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Temperature Range: Greases have different melting points and temperature limits depending on how they’re made. Choose a process that matches the environment in which your grease will be used.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Efficient Production: The process affects more than just the grease. The right choice helps factories run smoothly and minimize waste.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Finishing Steps Matter, Too\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"After the initial making, many grease companies go through a final smoothing process. This gives them the best uniform texture for easy application and reliable performance.\"}]}]','2024-08-09 05:38:27.023000','2024-08-09 05:38:29.642000','2024-08-09 05:38:29.634000',2,2,'2024-04-19'),(13,'Boost Your Profits with Smarter Lubrication and Metal Working Fluids','boost-your-profits-with-smarter-lubrication-and-metal-working-fluids','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Cutting Waste, Cutting Costs: How Smarter Lubrication and Metal Scrap Processing can be Greased.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Metal Working Fluids And Lubricants Give You Ways To Improve Profits\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In the competitive metalworking industry, every cost-saving and efficiency gain counts. Two often-overlooked areas with huge potential for improvement are metalworking fluids and lubricants and how you handle scrap metal.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let’s look at how these aspects can turn from expenses into profit centers.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Hidden Power of Lubrication\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Think of high-performance lubricants as the protectors of your expensive cutting tools. These specialized oils create a protective layer that shields your tools from wear and tear, extending their lifespan significantly. This means you won’t be replacing those expensive bits as often, and you’ll have less downtime due to tool changes or breakdowns.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Longer Tool Life\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Longer-Tool-Life.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Longer-Tool-Life.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Longer_Tool_Life_ce0208ff20.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Longer-Tool-Life.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Longer_Tool_Life_ce0208ff20\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":11.35,\"sizeInBytes\":11347,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Longer_Tool_Life_ce0208ff20.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Longer-Tool-Life.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Longer_Tool_Life_ce0208ff20\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":35.51,\"sizeInBytes\":35506,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Longer_Tool_Life_ce0208ff20.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Longer-Tool-Life.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Longer_Tool_Life_ce0208ff20\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":64.99,\"sizeInBytes\":64985,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Longer_Tool_Life_ce0208ff20.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Longer-Tool-Life.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Longer_Tool_Life_ce0208ff20\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":98.92,\"sizeInBytes\":98922,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Longer_Tool_Life_ce0208ff20.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Longer_Tool_Life_ce0208ff20\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":107.84,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-09T05:56:30.204Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-09T05:56:30.204Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Friction is the enemy of efficiency in metalworking. When things run smoothly, you can ramp up your machines to higher speeds without worrying about damaging your tools or sacrificing the quality of your work.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The result? You produce more parts in less time, boosting your overall output.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Not only does optimal lubrication protect your tools and speed up production, but it also saves you money on energy expenditures, which is a significant benefit. With metal cutting fluids, friction is reduced, which means that your machines will work less hard. The result is a reduction in the amount of money spent on power, which is always a good benefit.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let’s talk about the impeccable finish that your consumers want and demand and how you may save money on energy costs. It is possible to ensure that your tools will glide through the metal without any problem by using the appropriate lubricants. This will result in cuts that are exact, smooth, and have a superb surface finish. As a consequence of this, you will save both time and materials because you will spend less time reviewing items or doing additional finishing activities. This will allow you to save more time.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"If you choose the right lubricants for your metalworking operations, you will reap the benefits in a variety of ways, such as turning tools that have a longer lifespan, produce more output in a shorter amount of time, consume less energy, and have superior finishes. What a wonderful combination that is!\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Scrap Metal is a Potential Source of Income For You\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Scrap-metal-is-a-potential-source-of-income-for-you-1024x512.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Scrap-metal-is-a-potential-source-of-income-for-you-1024x512.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Scrap_metal_is_a_potential_source_of_income_for_you_1024x512_47ae47321c.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Scrap-metal-is-a-potential-source-of-income-for-you-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Scrap_metal_is_a_potential_source_of_income_for_you_1024x512_47ae47321c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":10.55,\"sizeInBytes\":10547,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Scrap_metal_is_a_potential_source_of_income_for_you_1024x512_47ae47321c.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Scrap-metal-is-a-potential-source-of-income-for-you-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Scrap_metal_is_a_potential_source_of_income_for_you_1024x512_47ae47321c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":38.42,\"sizeInBytes\":38420,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Scrap_metal_is_a_potential_source_of_income_for_you_1024x512_47ae47321c.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Scrap-metal-is-a-potential-source-of-income-for-you-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Scrap_metal_is_a_potential_source_of_income_for_you_1024x512_47ae47321c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":75.55,\"sizeInBytes\":75551,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Scrap_metal_is_a_potential_source_of_income_for_you_1024x512_47ae47321c.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Scrap-metal-is-a-potential-source-of-income-for-you-1024x512.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Scrap_metal_is_a_potential_source_of_income_for_you_1024x512_47ae47321c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":119.3,\"sizeInBytes\":119298,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Scrap_metal_is_a_potential_source_of_income_for_you_1024x512_47ae47321c.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Scrap_metal_is_a_potential_source_of_income_for_you_1024x512_47ae47321c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":131.83,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-09T05:57:33.804Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-09T05:57:33.804Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"For the sake of this discussion, let us overlook that scrap metal is nothing more than a waste problem. To put it another way, you could consider it a hidden source of financial advantage! When you make use of automated scrap processing equipment, you are provided with the resources that are required to convert those metal scraps into goods that are of value. In addition to being able to save money on the disposal of waste, you will also be able to produce new income by reselling the scrap that has been processed. This will allow you to both save money and generate new cash. When you recycle your scrap, you reduce the amount of fresh resources that need to be mined, which is a positive impact on the environment. In addition, let us not overlook the positive effects that this has on the environment.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It is true that the development of an automated scrap processing system requires a certain amount of investment; however, the long-term benefits greatly surpass the original expenditures. In other words, the expense of the first investment is not worth it. If you are interested in determining the approximate amount of money that you could be able to acquire, a reliable source can aid you in assessing the scrap that you are presently creating and calculating the projected returns. This will allow you to understand the potential amount of money that you could get. They will guide you through the entire process, ensuring that you choose the suitable technology and that you get the most out of your metal recycling program through their assistance. They will walk you through the entire procedure.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The All-Win Combination That Will Take the Cake\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The processing of scrap is accelerated while, at the same time, the lubrication is improved. The efficient running of your machines enables you to improve the rate at which you produce components of superior quality. While all of this is going on, the scrap bins you have are not only creating cash but also lessening the influence that you have on the environment. The possibility of this happening is not a pipe dream; rather, it is realistic in the event that manufacturers are prepared to accept these game-changing innovations.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It is important to keep in mind that even relatively simple improvements can have a significant impact on your bottom line. What you are able to accomplish today is as follows:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Inspection of Lubrication: Take into consideration the procedures that are now in place and identify places in which additional improvements could be made. To build tailored solutions, it is recommended to consult with an expert.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The options for scrap processing include investigating automated scrap handling systems and getting in touch with vendors in order to determine the potential return on investment for your operations.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Quantify the Impact: Determine the possible cost reductions and revenue acquisitions that could be achieved via the implementation of these initiatives. Your internal business case will be strengthened as a result of this.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Introducing Atlantic Lubricants\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Introducing-Atlantic-Lubricants.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Introducing-Atlantic-Lubricants.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Introducing_Atlantic_Lubricants_0dfdce664a.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Introducing-Atlantic-Lubricants.jpg\",\"hash