en\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Your workhorses are going to be these oils! Their ability to handle everything from heavy-duty cutting on thick steel to precision work on delicate metals is a testament to their ability to blend smoothly with water. Not only do they extend the lifespan of your cutting instruments, but they also guarantee that the operation will be smooth and in pristine condition.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic Neat Cutting Oils NCO-3:\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Especially if you work with non-ferrous metals like aluminum or copper, this is the option that caters to your needs in a variety of situations.  Additionally, it is an excellent tool for cutting certain kinds of steel. It is the mission of NCO-3 to ensure that everything runs smoothly; it cuts down on friction and ensures that your machines remain clean. The irritating mist that is present in your machinery is reduced as a result.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"What is the most enjoyable aspect? Atlantic oils are made with you in mind; apart from being potent and dependable, they are also simple to apply.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Future Looks Promising\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The metalworking industry is always undergoing change. Your ability to adapt your methods regarding lubrication and scrap management will ensure that you not only survive but also prosper. Do not allow your rivals to pursue you when you have the ability to take the lead by adopting metal working base oil resources that have been utilized.\"}]}]','2024-08-09 06:01:12.012000','2024-08-09 06:01:14.519000','2024-08-09 06:01:14.513000',2,2,'2024-03-06'),(14,'Diesel Engine Oil Storage Secrets for Garages and Shops','diesel-engine-oil-storage-secrets-for-garages-and-shops','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Modern engines demand attention. You need to consider the wide array of oil types and grades available. Proper storage and handling are essential to avoid mix-ups and ensure your vehicle runs smoothly. Here are some garage-savvy tips from Atlantic to help you out.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Storage Savvy:\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Modern engines mean more oil choices. Master those different types and grades! Proper storage is key to avoid mix-ups and keep your engine happy. For storage, think cool and dry – basements or sheds work great. Hot rooms? That’s bad news for oil. Sunlight is no friend either – keep your oil out of direct light. And remember, safety first! Oil and sparks don’t mix, so store it away from electrical gear and anything hazardous.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Container Check:\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When your bulk synthetic diesel engine oil arrives, check it over! Reject anything leaky, dented, or off. Keep oils sealed in their original containers. This prevents contamination and keeps everything pure. A messy space means a messy mind. Use shelves, racks, or bins to organize your oils. You’ll save time and avoid confusion. Label everything clearly – oil type, viscosity, and API category. Don’t mix things up!\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Use older oil first. This ensures it doesn’t lose its punch before you need it. Think of it like a first-in, first-out system. Everything gets used at its best, and no oil goes to waste. This gives your customers the best engine performance possible. Everything runs smoothly, just like a well-oiled machine! Plus, you save money in the long run.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Label Like a Pro:\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"You might think labeling is overkill, but trust me – mark every tank, dispenser, everything! Include the oil’s name, viscosity, and performance level. This little step saves you from big headaches down the road. Do regular stock checks. Toss outdated oils. Newer CK-4 oils often work in older engines – that means you can streamline your inventory and ditch the clutter. Less oil, less confusion, happier customers!\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Diesel Engine Fluids Have a Special Case:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Diesel-Engine-Fluids-Have-a-Special-Case.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Diesel-Engine-Fluids-Have-a-Special-Case.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Diesel_Engine_Fluids_Have_a_Special_Case_774ffa4237.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Diesel-Engine-Fluids-Have-a-Special-Case.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Diesel_Engine_Fluids_Have_a_Special_Case_774ffa4237\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":9.77,\"sizeInBytes\":9774,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Diesel_Engine_Fluids_Have_a_Special_Case_774ffa4237.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Diesel-Engine-Fluids-Have-a-Special-Case.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Diesel_Engine_Fluids_Have_a_Special_Case_774ffa4237\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":56.85,\"sizeInBytes\":56853,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Diesel_Engine_Fluids_Have_a_Special_Case_774ffa4237.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Diesel-Engine-Fluids-Have-a-Special-Case.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Diesel_Engine_Fluids_Have_a_Special_Case_774ffa4237\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":30.84,\"sizeInBytes\":30836,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Diesel_Engine_Fluids_Have_a_Special_Case_774ffa4237.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Diesel-Engine-Fluids-Have-a-Special-Case.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Diesel_Engine_Fluids_Have_a_Special_Case_774ffa4237\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":86.74,\"sizeInBytes\":86742,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Diesel_Engine_Fluids_Have_a_Special_Case_774ffa4237.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Diesel_Engine_Fluids_Have_a_Special_Case_774ffa4237\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":95.18,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-09T06:43:46.534Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-09T06:43:46.534Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Heavy duty diesel engine oil needs the best care. Keep it in the original container at room temp – no freezing, no baking! Remember, DEF has a shelf life (about 18 months). Use the oldest stuff first so you don’t get stuck with expired DEF.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Switching to new oils? Plan ahead and tell your team! A smooth transition means everyone’s in the loop. Before the new oil arrives, clean your bulk tanks. A fresh start is important! And I know I sound like a broken record, but label those dispensers! This little detail saves you from big headaches and mix-ups\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Shop Streamlining:\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Label Like Crazy: Seems basic, but mark those tanks, tools, everything! Include the oil’s name, viscosity, and performance level. This saves you major headaches later.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Out with the Old, In with the Versatile: Check your stock regularly. Toss outdated oils! Newer CK-4 oils often work in older engines, so you can ditch the clutter. Less oil means less confusion – and happier customers.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Change is Coming: Switching oils? Plan ahead, tell your team! Smooth transitions need good communication. Before the new stuff arrives, clean those bulk tanks. A fresh start is key!\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Labeling – The Golden Rule: I’ll say it again – label those dispensers! This little detail prevents expensive mistakes. Label like your shop’s life depends on it!\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Beyond Storage:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Beyond-Storage-Be-Prepared.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Beyond-Storage-Be-Prepared.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Beyond_Storage_Be_Prepared_0d6f971950.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Beyond-Storage-Be-Prepared.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Beyond_Storage_Be_Prepared_0d6f971950\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":8.86,\"sizeInBytes\":8862,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Beyond_Storage_Be_Prepared_0d6f971950.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Beyond-Storage-Be-Prepared.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Beyond_Storage_Be_Prepared_0d6f971950\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":52.38,\"sizeInBytes\":52383,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Beyond_Storage_Be_Prepared_0d6f971950.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Beyond-Storage-Be-Prepared.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Beyond_Storage_Be_Prepared_0d6f971950\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":28.18,\"sizeInBytes\":28178,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Beyond_Storage_Be_Prepared_0d6f971950.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Beyond-Storage-Be-Prepared.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Beyond_Storage_Be_Prepared_0d6f971950\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":80.48,\"sizeInBytes\":80478,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Beyond_Storage_Be_Prepared_0d6f971950.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Beyond_Storage_Be_Prepared_0d6f971950\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":88.75,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-09T06:45:44.198Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-09T06:45:44.198Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Your shop’s foundation is the oil storage system\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In order to become an expert in engine care, the first step is to store the oil properly. Teach your technicians to become oil specialists! They will be familiar with the appropriate oils, manage them with care, and impeccably apply them. This prevents you from making costly mistakes and ensures that your engines continue to run smoothly.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Be Prepared for What May Come Your Way!\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"A messy fact is that spills occur. Drip pans should be placed under dispensers, and absorbent materials should be available. Clean up spills as quickly as possible is healthier for the environment and your sanity.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It Is Important to Maintain\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In the same way that your clients’ automobiles require maintenance, your oil storage facility does as well. Make sure to check your storage space, dispensers, and tanks on a regular basis. In the early stages, detect any leaks, corrosion, or worn-out equipment. Fixing those little issues now can save you a lot of difficulties in the future.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Responsibility in Disposal- The Final Step in the Process\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Leaving used oil and empty containers in the environment is not something that has to be done. Find recyclers who are permitted to do so or follow the standards that govern appropriate disposal in your area. Please do what you can, and the entire planet will be grateful to you — one contented and well-lubricated engine at a time!\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Be A Savvy Oil Expert\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Be-A-Savvy-Oil-Expert.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Be-A-Savvy-Oil-Expert.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Be_A_Savvy_Oil_Expert_73ac11e73c.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Be-A-Savvy-Oil-Expert.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Be_A_Savvy_Oil_Expert_73ac11e73c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":9.53,\"sizeInBytes\":9529,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Be_A_Savvy_Oil_Expert_73ac11e73c.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Be-A-Savvy-Oil-Expert.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Be_A_Savvy_Oil_Expert_73ac11e73c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":49.32,\"sizeInBytes\":49321,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Be_A_Savvy_Oil_Expert_73ac11e73c.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Be-A-Savvy-Oil-Expert.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Be_A_Savvy_Oil_Expert_73ac11e73c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":27.48,\"sizeInBytes\":27476,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Be_A_Savvy_Oil_Expert_73ac11e73c.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Be-A-Savvy-Oil-Expert.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Be_A_Savvy_Oil_Expert_73ac11e73c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":74.59,\"sizeInBytes\":74591,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Be_A_Savvy_Oil_Expert_73ac11e73c.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Be_A_Savvy_Oil_Expert_73ac11e73c\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":81.15,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-09T06:47:19.149Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-09T06:47:19.149Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Building a Culture of Oil Care: Going Beyond Organizational Structures\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Not only do these behaviors promote a culture of oil knowledge, but they also make the shelves more organized from the inside out. Not only does your store function efficiently, but you also contribute to a more environmentally friendly future. Mastering oil storage and handling is about doing activities in a responsible manner that are to everyone’s benefit.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"You are the Champion of Oil Handling in your Shop\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"You will see a transformation in your store if you follow these guidelines. In addition to the fact that those engines will operate without a hitch, your workstation will also be effective and well-organized. There is certainly cause for celebration here!\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"A Little TLC for Your Oil Equipment\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Regular maintenance is required for your oil storage, just like it is for those client autos. Inspect everything, even dispensers, and tanks! In the early stages, detect leaks, corrosion, and worn components. Fixing minor issues today will prevent major issues in the future.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Utilized Oil: Don’t Throw Away the Environment\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Containers that have been emptied and utilized oil require careful handling. Investigate the local regulations, locate the approved recyclers, and do your part! Everybody comes out ahead when it comes to responsible disposal.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]}]','2024-08-09 06:49:42.685000','2024-08-09 06:50:39.525000','2024-08-09 06:49:45.195000',2,2,'2024-02-21'),(15,'Industrial Lubricant Oils Ensure the Smooth Rolling of Machine Work','industrial-lubricant-oils-ensure-the-smooth-rolling-of-machine-work','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Lubricants serve as indispensable components in numerous applications, minimizing friction and wear in numerous industries where they go unnoticed. Rolling metal wires are a prominent example of one of these applications; it guarantees high-quality wire products and effortless production.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Critical Importance Of Lubricant Oils In The Industry\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"A wire-making organization specializing in metal wire production operates its rolling mills with lubricant oils. By forming an essential barrier between the wire, these lubricants significantly reduce heat generation and friction that occurs during the process. Lubrication serves to guarantee seamless operation, avert wire defects, and ultimately enhance production efficiency while contributing to the generation of superior final products.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Confronting The Obstacle: The Impact Of Oil Contamination And Its Effects\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Lubricant oils, notwithstanding their critical function, are vulnerable to contamination. Owing to oxidation byproducts and metal detritus, minuscule particles can gradually accumulate in the oil. The following contaminants present a substantial peril to the wire drawing procedure:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Wire Damage: The wire surface may sustain scratches or gouges caused by contaminants, which may result in defects and even product failure.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Production Interruptions: The accumulation of impurities may cause operational disturbances in the rolling mills, leading to cessation of production and subsequent time loss.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Damaged wires resulting from contamination frequently end up as refuse, which results in material waste and escalated production expenses.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Emerging Approach\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"The-Emerging-Approach-Regular-Oil-Replacements.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"The-Emerging-Approach-Regular-Oil-Replacements.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/The_Emerging_Approach_Regular_Oil_Replacements_d1ae91680a.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_The-Emerging-Approach-Regular-Oil-Replacements.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_The_Emerging_Approach_Regular_Oil_Replacements_d1ae91680a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":9.4,\"sizeInBytes\":9400,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_The_Emerging_Approach_Regular_Oil_Replacements_d1ae91680a.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_The-Emerging-Approach-Regular-Oil-Replacements.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_The_Emerging_Approach_Regular_Oil_Replacements_d1ae91680a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":49.29,\"sizeInBytes\":49291,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_The_Emerging_Approach_Regular_Oil_Replacements_d1ae91680a.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_The-Emerging-Approach-Regular-Oil-Replacements.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_The_Emerging_Approach_Regular_Oil_Replacements_d1ae91680a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":27.26,\"sizeInBytes\":27261,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_The_Emerging_Approach_Regular_Oil_Replacements_d1ae91680a.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_The-Emerging-Approach-Regular-Oil-Replacements.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_The_Emerging_Approach_Regular_Oil_Replacements_d1ae91680a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":74.16,\"sizeInBytes\":74159,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_The_Emerging_Approach_Regular_Oil_Replacements_d1ae91680a.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"The_Emerging_Approach_Regular_Oil_Replacements_d1ae91680a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":80.73,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-09T07:52:43.231Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-09T07:52:43.231Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In order to address these obstacles, numerous other businesses conventionally utilized filtration techniques to eliminate impurities from their lubricant oils. Nonetheless, these techniques frequently fail to capture extremely minute or light particles. \"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Insufficient Cleansing: The oil retained minute contaminants, which progressively accumulated into a concentrated “sludge” that presented even more severe hazards.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Regular Oil Replacements: As a consequence of inadequate cleansing, frequent oil changes are required, leading to escalated operational expenses and environmental repercussions.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"An Innovative Oil Cleaning System Is Introduced\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In light of the constraints associated with conventional approaches, the research has adopted a novel resolution: the oil cleansing system. Sophisticated in design, this system explicitly targets the problem of oil contamination in wire drawing applications. A multi-stage process is utilized to efficiently eliminate particles that are overlooked by conventional filtration and centrifuges:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Coagulation: Initiates the formation of larger concentrations of fine particles that are readily captured by filters by means of special chemicals that induce clumping.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In microfiltration, specialized filters with exceedingly minute apertures are employed, enabling the capture of even the most minute particles of contaminants.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Degassing under vacuum: Eliminates dissolved gasses and air pockets from the oil, thereby enhancing its lubricating capabilities.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Life Cycle Assessment: Figuring Out The Effects On The Environment\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The oil cleaning system does a lot of good for the world. A Life Cycle Assessment (LCA) study done in Sweden looked at how two different situations would affect the environment: The original system used traditional filtering methods and changed the oil often. Systems with an oil cleaning system use a new cleaning technology that uses less oil. The study was mostly about three types of impacts:\"}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Global Warming Potential (GWP): The amount of greenhouse gasses released when the system works and oil is used.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Acidifying Potential (AP): Emissions that make the air more acidic, mostly sulfur oxides and nitrogen oxides.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"What is Human Toxicity Potential (HTP)? HTP is the chance that pollutants in the world will poison people.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Findings Were Very Interesting:\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Significant Reduction in Environmental Effects: Compared to the original system, the oil cleaning system had about a 90% reduction in all three types of environmental effects.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Equivalent to Less Oil Use: This drop is a direct result of less oil being used because the system makes oil last longer.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Taking Into Account Effects And Looking Into More Benefits\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Weighting factors based on well-known methods like EDIP97 can be used to figure out how important each impact area is in comparison to the others. The most important thing to worry about here is the possibility of global warming.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"But there are more possible solutions to this.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Reusing The Waste Oil:\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Reusing-The-Waste-Oil.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Reusing-The-Waste-Oil.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Reusing_The_Waste_Oil_c92a7c267d.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Reusing-The-Waste-Oil.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Reusing_The_Waste_Oil_c92a7c267d\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":9.73,\"sizeInBytes\":9733,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Reusing_The_Waste_Oil_c92a7c267d.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Reusing-The-Waste-Oil.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Reusing_The_Waste_Oil_c92a7c267d\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":55.36,\"sizeInBytes\":55355,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Reusing_The_Waste_Oil_c92a7c267d.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Reusing-The-Waste-Oil.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Reusing_The_Waste_Oil_c92a7c267d\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":29.93,\"sizeInBytes\":29933,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Reusing_The_Waste_Oil_c92a7c267d.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Reusing-The-Waste-Oil.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Reusing_The_Waste_Oil_c92a7c267d\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":83.84,\"sizeInBytes\":83836,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Reusing_The_Waste_Oil_c92a7c267d.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Reusing_The_Waste_Oil_c92a7c267d\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":92.12,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-09T07:57:33.387Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-09T07:57:33.387Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The machine lubricant oil effect will be smaller if the used oil is re-refined instead of burnt. This practice will show the benefits to the economy.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Further, the new study shows that using clean energy sources and properly managing waste can have an even greater positive impact on the ecosystem. This is related to industrial oil as well.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Thing Of Sustainability In The Lubricant Industry:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Using lubricants for both the planet and your wallet is a modern approach to many industrial works, especially the automotive industry.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Being “green” isn’t just good for the Earth; it’s good for business, too. Companies are increasingly realizing that sustainability is key to their success, and the industrial lubricants industry is no exception. But how can we make these oils more eco-friendly without sacrificing performance or breaking the bank?\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Seeing The Big Picture Of The Future:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Before developing new lubricants, companies need to understand their entire environmental impact, from the resources used to make them disposed of. The life cycle assessment shows how the oil will charge hidden environmental costs. By doing LCAs, companies can avoid simply shifting problems around, like creating pollution in one area while reducing it in another. They also help ensure future generations have the resources they will need.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Measuring The Impact Of Footprints\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Usually, there are two things to look for: footprint and handprint. The prior has a negative impact on the environment, and the other is attributed to a positive impact.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Ideally, we want to minimize the footprint while maximizing the handprint. For petrochemical industrial lubricants, this means designing them to be more eco-friendly while still exceeding performance expectations.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Three Paths To Sustainable Lubricants\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Three-Paths-To-Sustainable-Lubricants.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Three-Paths-To-Sustainable-Lubricants.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Three_Paths_To_Sustainable_Lubricants_014951339a.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Three-Paths-To-Sustainable-Lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Three_Paths_To_Sustainable_Lubricants_014951339a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":10.35,\"sizeInBytes\":10354,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Three_Paths_To_Sustainable_Lubricants_014951339a.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Three-Paths-To-Sustainable-Lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Three_Paths_To_Sustainable_Lubricants_014951339a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":64.5,\"sizeInBytes\":64495,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Three_Paths_To_Sustainable_Lubricants_014951339a.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Three-Paths-To-Sustainable-Lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Three_Paths_To_Sustainable_Lubricants_014951339a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":97.21,\"sizeInBytes\":97209,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Three_Paths_To_Sustainable_Lubricants_014951339a.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Three-Paths-To-Sustainable-Lubricants.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Three_Paths_To_Sustainable_Lubricants_014951339a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":34.25,\"sizeInBytes\":34249,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Three_Paths_To_Sustainable_Lubricants_014951339a.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Three_Paths_To_Sustainable_Lubricants_014951339a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":106.56,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-09T09:01:04.093Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-09T09:01:04.093Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"So, how does Atlantic manufacture these dream industrial lubricants for Dubai? Here are three key approaches:\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Low-Impact Design:\",\"bold\":true},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" This means using fewer resources and opting for eco-friendly materials, like bio-lubricants. These oils are especially popular for sensitive areas like forests and waterways, as they biodegrade quickly and pose minimal harm to wildlife.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Energy-Efficient Performance:\",\"bold\":true},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" Lubricants can play a part in reducing energy consumption by minimizing friction and wear in machinery. By using special-performance polymers, we can create lubricants that keep things running smoothly while using less energy.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Longer Lifespan:\",\"bold\":true},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" Frequent oil changes are wasteful and expensive. By developing additive packages that extend the life of lubricants, we can reduce waste and save money.\"}]}]','2024-08-09 09:02:20.149000','2024-08-09 09:02:23.922000','2024-08-09 09:02:23.917000',2,2,'2024-02-12'),(16,'Car Care Products Profit Up and Master the Art of Detailing','car-care-products-profit-up-and-master-the-art-of-detailing','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"So, you’ve got a passion for cars and want to give them a wash and shine with a garage stocked with enough detailing products to make Mary Poppins jealous. You’re a car expert, like an alchemist of swirl removal and shine. But let’s face it, turning that automotive passion into a self-detailing vehicle requires more than just a killer hand with a car care product. You need to master the art of detailing to weave your love for cars into a needlepoint of satisfaction and, yes, on a low budget.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Forget high-pressure strategies and cheesy car salesman grins. We’re not about sleaze, we’re about Always Be Closing,and believe me, that doesn’t mean strong-arming their car into a ceramic coating they don’t need. ABC stands for something far more profound: Additional Benefit Creation. It’s about understanding your desires, crafting solutions that fit like a tailored seat cover, and leaving you feeling like you just stumbled into the automotive equivalent of Willy Wonka’s factory.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Befriend the Beast, Not Just the Bucks\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Forget sales pitches and cheesy greetings, Atlantic believes your car deserves more. We see your automotive is a reflection of your passion, waiting to be polished to perfection. Drop the tired cliches and greet car owners like true enthusiasts, eyes gleaming at the thought of a flawlessly buffed hood spotting the sunset. Lean in, listen to their car’s whispers – the swirl of stories etched by the sun, the furnishings moaning under bird-bomb battles. These aren’t just scuffs and stains, they’re anxieties holding back‌ love for their four-wheeled companion.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic isn’t here to just market products. We offer the keys to automotive bliss. Imagine your car transformed –purring with newfound pride, its paint reflecting the open road like a pristine mirror. By becoming a trusted car care confidante, we’ll transform a transaction into a satisfying makeover, a journey where anxieties fade, and car love shines. Atlantic gives the best versions of your machines, one perfect shine at a time, in the shape of wholesale car care products.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Diagnose the problem!\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let’s face it, your car deserves more than a quick hose-down and a prayer. It’s a loyal companion, a reflection of your style, and a gateway to open roads and endless adventures. But is it living up to its full potential? Is it shimmering with pride or sighing under a cloak of dust and grime?\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"At Atlantic, we believe every car deserves to be treated like a goddess, pampered with the finest care products, and sent out into the world radiating confidence. We’re not about quick fixes or empty promises. We’re car-care alchemists, transforming tired beasts into gleaming visions of automotive perfection.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"But before we whip out the magic potions, let’s have a heart-to-heart with your four-wheeled friend. Forget scripted pitches and robotic greetings. We’ll listen intently to your car’s whispers – the swirl stories etched by the sun, the leather murmurs yearning for rejuvenation, the tires pleading for a touch of shine.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Because you see, it’s not just about dirt and grime, it’s about anxieties holding back your automotive love. Is that stubborn stain a battle scar lost forever? Can that sun-bleached interior ever regain its youthful glow? We say, “Challenge accepted!”\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Think of us as your car-care confidantes. We’ll reveal the perfect solutions, manufacturing personalized products that go beyond a mere list of products. We recommend Atlantic solutions, each product carefully chosen to resonate with your car’s distinctive demands.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Imagine the transformation:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Imagine-the-transformation.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Imagine-the-transformation.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Imagine_the_transformation_95cecde57a.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Imagine-the-transformation.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Imagine_the_transformation_95cecde57a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":8.94,\"sizeInBytes\":8938,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Imagine_the_transformation_95cecde57a.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Imagine-the-transformation.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Imagine_the_transformation_95cecde57a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":46.65,\"sizeInBytes\":46645,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Imagine_the_transformation_95cecde57a.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Imagine-the-transformation.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Imagine_the_transformation_95cecde57a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":25.4,\"sizeInBytes\":25403,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Imagine_the_transformation_95cecde57a.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Imagine-the-transformation.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Imagine_the_transformation_95cecde57a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":73.61,\"sizeInBytes\":73613,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Imagine_the_transformation_95cecde57a.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Imagine_the_transformation_95cecde57a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":82.88,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-09T09:45:49.924Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-09T09:45:49.924Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic Wash & Shine: \"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"A gentle caress that washes away the dust of ordinary and leaves behind a dazzling, mirror-like finish. Watch water bead off like liquid diamonds, revealing the true depth and vibrancy of your car’s color.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic Leather Protection Spray:\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Atlantic-Leather-Protection-Spray-Tyre-Shiner.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Atlantic-Leather-Protection-Spray-Tyre-Shiner.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Atlantic_Leather_Protection_Spray_Tyre_Shiner_4c9ebacaff.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Atlantic-Leather-Protection-Spray-Tyre-Shiner.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Atlantic_Leather_Protection_Spray_Tyre_Shiner_4c9ebacaff\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":11.54,\"sizeInBytes\":11542,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Atlantic_Leather_Protection_Spray_Tyre_Shiner_4c9ebacaff.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Atlantic-Leather-Protection-Spray-Tyre-Shiner.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Atlantic_Leather_Protection_Spray_Tyre_Shiner_4c9ebacaff\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":n