elivers a crystal-clear windshield that gives a glimpse of a flawless view out of your car. With the clear windshield, every drop of rain becomes the fleeting jewel that is sparkling in the sunlight.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"These are just a few products ‌that Atlantic offers. We offer a comprehensive range of products, each one expertly formulated to address the specific needs of your car care. But remember, this is not just about the local car care products;this is about your passion for the automotive. We understand the emotional bond between you and your car, and we are here to help you nurture that love bond and give you one gleaming detail at a time.\"}]}]','2024-08-09 09:47:56.918000','2024-08-09 09:49:47.461000','2024-08-09 09:48:00.109000',2,2,'2024-01-29'),(17,'The Ideal Usage Of Lubricants And Greases For Maintaining Machine Performance','the-ideal-usage-of-lubricants-and-greases-for-maintaining-machine-performance','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In the machinery world, greases and lubricants are ‌the secrets of a machine’s long life and smooth running. It saves money and time by not needing to be maintained, go-after go.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"We all know that greases and lubricants are for the smoothness of machines and tools for industries, mainly for cars and automobiles. So, how to get their perfection, never-ending and long time is the quest for the modern world. Atlantic has the answer in the shape of specialty chemical greases and lubricants for all-purpose use.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Think of lubricants and grease as the lifeblood of mechanical systems. Every moving part demands a perfect match, from the smallest cogs to the mightiest engines. Choosing the right product is like matchmaking in the mechanical world – get it right, and you’ll hear the harmonious purr of a well-oiled machine. So, let’s get down to the nitty-gritty and talk about the different types of greases and lubricants and when you, the master of machines, should use them.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Multipurpose Marvel: Mineral Oil-Based Lubricants\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Starting with the jack-of-all-trades, mineral oil-based lubricants are the workhorses of the lubricant world. They’re derived from refining crude oil and are versatile enough to be used in engines, transmissions, and gearboxes. If you’re after a reliable, cost-effective solution, these lubricants are your go-to option.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Grease Is A Spectrum Of Slipperiness\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"The-Grease-Is-A-Spectrum-of-Slipperiness.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"The-Grease-Is-A-Spectrum-of-Slipperiness.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/The_Grease_Is_A_Spectrum_of_Slipperiness_67f0f89a1b.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_The-Grease-Is-A-Spectrum-of-Slipperiness.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_The_Grease_Is_A_Spectrum_of_Slipperiness_67f0f89a1b\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":10.14,\"sizeInBytes\":10138,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_The_Grease_Is_A_Spectrum_of_Slipperiness_67f0f89a1b.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_The-Grease-Is-A-Spectrum-of-Slipperiness.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_The_Grease_Is_A_Spectrum_of_Slipperiness_67f0f89a1b\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":65.91,\"sizeInBytes\":65910,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_The_Grease_Is_A_Spectrum_of_Slipperiness_67f0f89a1b.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_The-Grease-Is-A-Spectrum-of-Slipperiness.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_The_Grease_Is_A_Spectrum_of_Slipperiness_67f0f89a1b\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":102.28,\"sizeInBytes\":102275,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_The_Grease_Is_A_Spectrum_of_Slipperiness_67f0f89a1b.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_The-Grease-Is-A-Spectrum-of-Slipperiness.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_The_Grease_Is_A_Spectrum_of_Slipperiness_67f0f89a1b\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":34.62,\"sizeInBytes\":34623,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_The_Grease_Is_A_Spectrum_of_Slipperiness_67f0f89a1b.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"The_Grease_Is_A_Spectrum_of_Slipperiness_67f0f89a1b\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":112.38,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-10T06:09:21.604Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-10T06:09:21.604Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"From the roar of your car’s engine to the hum of industrial gear, every moving part begs for the right type of grease. It’s a diverse universe out there, and no two lubricants are created equal. They come with their unique personalities, each offering a different tune to the music of motion.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Synthetic Specialist: Customized Chemical Mastery\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Synthetic lubricants are the tailored suits of the lubrication world. Engineered from specific chemicals, they’re designed to perform under extreme conditions that would leave conventional oils in the dust. Whether you’re dealing with high temperatures or seeking ultimate performance, synthetic lubricants are your high-tech choice.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Calcium Crusader\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let’s kick things off with Calcium Grease, a classic, like the Beatles of Grease. It’s the all-rounder with a penchant for water resistance and corrosion protection. It’s got a firm handshake – that’s mechanical stability for you – and it’s ready to perform at lower temperatures. If your gear is taking a swim in marine, industrial, farming, or low-heat automotive applications, this is your go-to.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Bio-Based Buddy: Eco-Friendly And Engine-Friendly\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"The-Bio-Based-Buddy-Eco-Friendly-and-Engine-Friendly.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"The-Bio-Based-Buddy-Eco-Friendly-and-Engine-Friendly.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/The_Bio_Based_Buddy_Eco_Friendly_and_Engine_Friendly_8e7633eb0e.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_The-Bio-Based-Buddy-Eco-Friendly-and-Engine-Friendly.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_The_Bio_Based_Buddy_Eco_Friendly_and_Engine_Friendly_8e7633eb0e\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":10.99,\"sizeInBytes\":10986,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_The_Bio_Based_Buddy_Eco_Friendly_and_Engine_Friendly_8e7633eb0e.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_The-Bio-Based-Buddy-Eco-Friendly-and-Engine-Friendly.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_The_Bio_Based_Buddy_Eco_Friendly_and_Engine_Friendly_8e7633eb0e\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":34.86,\"sizeInBytes\":34856,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_The_Bio_Based_Buddy_Eco_Friendly_and_Engine_Friendly_8e7633eb0e.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_The-Bio-Based-Buddy-Eco-Friendly-and-Engine-Friendly.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_The_Bio_Based_Buddy_Eco_Friendly_and_Engine_Friendly_8e7633eb0e\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":64.44,\"sizeInBytes\":64436,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_The_Bio_Based_Buddy_Eco_Friendly_and_Engine_Friendly_8e7633eb0e.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_The-Bio-Based-Buddy-Eco-Friendly-and-Engine-Friendly.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_The_Bio_Based_Buddy_Eco_Friendly_and_Engine_Friendly_8e7633eb0e\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":98.31,\"sizeInBytes\":98310,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_The_Bio_Based_Buddy_Eco_Friendly_and_Engine_Friendly_8e7633eb0e.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"The_Bio_Based_Buddy_Eco_Friendly_and_Engine_Friendly_8e7633eb0e\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":107.65,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-10T06:12:00.600Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-10T06:12:00.600Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"As we turn towards sustainability, bio-based lubricants are stepping into the spotlight. Made from vegetable oils and other renewable resources, they offer excellent lubricity with a smaller environmental footprint. If you’re eco-conscious and want your machinery to be as green as it is, bio-based lubricants are your environmental allies.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Aluminum Ace\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Moving on to aluminum complex grease, this one’s like an all-in-one solution. It can handle the heat, laugh in the face of water, and ward off rust like it’s nobody’s business. This grease shines in the food industry, where cleanliness is king, but it also wears many hats, serving the automotive, steel milling, construction, and farming sectors with equal aplomb.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Grease For The Toughest Tasks\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When it comes to withstanding heavy loads and preventing metal-to-metal contact, best grease for gears is your steadfast defender. It’s thicker than traditional oil and stays put under the harshest conditions, making it ideal for heavy-duty applications in construction and mining.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Barium Battalion\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Barium complex grease is the heavy lifter, perfect for when the going gets tough. It’s a high-performance trooper known for its steadfast mechanical stability, high-temperature resilience, and swift speed adaptability. Industries where the weight of the world is a literal problem, like aeronautical, marine, and manufacturing, will find a reliable partner in barium-complex grease.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Bentonite (Clay) Brigade\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now, let’s talk about bentonite grease. This clay-based maverick is known for its “non-melt” personality. It’s the James Bond of grease – cool under pressure and adaptable to temperature swings. It’s got the grip of a vice with its shear stability and adhesiveness, making it a prime candidate for the steel, manufacturing, and ceramic industries.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Polyurea Powerhouse For Machine\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Polyurea grease is a new kind of powerhouse for machines and automobiles. It’s making a space with its amazing versatility and high-temperature prowess. We can say that it is a long-term solution for plants, industries, and motors that offers solid protection against rust and wear. This is something necessary for every work.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Sodium Greases\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The third kind of grease is sodium grease. It is the traditionalists of the bunch that provide solid rust protection and a high dropping point. However, it is not friendly to water and is mostly seen hanging on the contact bearings, often blending with other greases to make up the game.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Additives That Contribute To Their Performance\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Additives-that-contribute-to-their-performance.jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"Additives-that-contribute-to-their-performance.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Additives_that_contribute_to_their_performance_8fc9b14799.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1024,\"height\":512,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Additives-that-contribute-to-their-performance.jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Additives_that_contribute_to_their_performance_8fc9b14799\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":122,\"size\":8.64,\"sizeInBytes\":8641,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Additives_that_contribute_to_their_performance_8fc9b14799.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Additives-that-contribute-to-their-performance.jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_Additives_that_contribute_to_their_performance_8fc9b14799\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":48.51,\"sizeInBytes\":48512,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Additives_that_contribute_to_their_performance_8fc9b14799.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Additives-that-contribute-to-their-performance.jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_Additives_that_contribute_to_their_performance_8fc9b14799\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":26.56,\"sizeInBytes\":26555,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Additives_that_contribute_to_their_performance_8fc9b14799.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Additives-that-contribute-to-their-performance.jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_Additives_that_contribute_to_their_performance_8fc9b14799\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":74.08,\"sizeInBytes\":74082,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Additives_that_contribute_to_their_performance_8fc9b14799.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"Additives_that_contribute_to_their_performance_8fc9b14799\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":81.18,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-08-10T06:15:42.906Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-08-10T06:15:42.906Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The difference between grease and lubricants is that they don’t work alone; they need speciality chemicals as additives for their best performance in the motor or industry. anti-wear additives are secret agents that work secretly with lubricants or greases to minimize ‌wear and tear. These chemicals make sure that your machines stay in top-notch conditions for a long time.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Corrosion And Rust Controller\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Corrosion inhibitors within lubricants are like the shield barriers that protect your machinery parts from the ravages of rust and corrosion. These are essential allies in the fight against ‌elements like water and oxidation. Thus, using them means you don’t compromise on machine integrity.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Friction And Heat Controller\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When friction comes, heat comes as well. High-quality lubricants and greases are designed to reduce friction, keeping the operating temperature down and performance up. These agents in your machines are not just running machines cool but get you rid of friction.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Atlantic Advantage\"}],\"level\":3},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When you reach for an Atlantic greasy, you’re not just choosing a product; you’re choosing a legacy of excellence. The key qualities of Atlantic greases and lubricants are born from rigorous research and development. They offer superior protection, enhanced performance, and unparalleled reliability. With a range of products designed to meet various technical specifications, Atlantic greases provide the right balance of base oils, additives, and thickeners to deliver outstanding results.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic has got your back whether you’re looking for grease lubricant that can withstand extreme pressures, operate in a wide range of temperatures, or maintain its integrity in corrosive environments. Their products are engineered to reduce wear and tear, extend the life of your equipment, and maximize efficiency for bearings.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In essence, grease and lubricants are the unsung heroes of any mechanical operation. They are the silent warriors that fight friction, wear, and corrosion day in and day out. So, next time you’re looking to keep your machinery in tip-top shape, remember to choose wisely because the right grease can mean the difference between an engine that purrs and one that stutters. With Atlantic’s high-quality greases and lubricants, you’re not just maintaining machines; you’re engineering excellence.\"}]}]','2024-08-10 06:17:07.528000','2024-08-10 06:17:09.976000','2024-08-10 06:17:09.969000',2,2,'2024-01-09'),(18,'Master The Art Of Shift Smoothly With Manual Transmission Oil','master-the-art-of-shift-smoothly-with-manual-transmission-oil','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Gearboxes in cars are dependent on their oils to provide smooth shifts while on the road. This product is important for the operational benefits of gearboxes.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Manual gearboxes in contrast to conventional motor oils are designed for engines. They are specifically designed to protect the gearboxes from rust and tear and other components that make up gearboxes. Since their introduction to the market, manual gearbox oil has experienced a significant shift and evolution towards advancements. The result is that today’s gearbox oils are highly specialized and have evolved to cater to the demands of modern automotive gears.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"There are a considerable number of advantages to using automotive gearbox oils. But this is only associated with the best performance oils from a leading company. This is so it provides improved lubrication, which guarantees that gears will function without any hiccups, without taking into account their working in high temperatures from a cold start. It is possible that the higher lubricating capacity can minimize the internal friction, results will be in the shape of less wear on the gearbox. Moreover, high lubrication leads to longer gearbox life and few repairs. As a result of smooth performance, the engine load is reduced, which leads to improved fuel economy.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In a variety of automotives, automatic & manual transmission oils are utilized extensively. They are essential for automobiles that have gearboxes, which include motorcyclists, high-performance race cars, and daily passenger cars.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In the automotive industry, they are also essential for motorbikes. In the aircraft industry, where precision and dependability in gear operation are of the utmost importance, as well as in the manufacturing sector, where machinery that demands consistent mechanical gearbox performance is required, their application is widespread.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Attention to details of Synthetic Automotive Gearbox Oils from Atlantic Grease and Lubricants\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"There is a huge variety of gearbox oils available from Atlantic Grease and Lubricants. These oils are designed to meet the specific needs of modern applications. The products are divided into categories according to their use and the cars. Their intended meanings are the same to improve the efficiency and durability of gearbox systems.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"For example, automotive gearbox oils are available in different varieties of viscosity grades. As an illustration, the company offers automotive manual gearbox lubricants in an extensive selection of viscosity grades to suit a variety of driving conditions and vehicle specifications. Designed to accommodate a vast array of vehicles, from high-performance sports cars to compact sedans, these lubricants are adaptable. There exists a potentiality that these lubricants comprise unique components that enhance gear protection, prolong the gearbox’s lifetime, and promote seamless shifting.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic’s manual gearbox lubricants are specifically engineered to withstand the demanding operational conditions and heavy loads that are customary in manufacturing machinery. A considerable proportion of these products are endowed with patented technology that preserves viscosity and is resistant to thermal degradation, even under the extreme strain that industrial gearboxes endure.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"An In-depth Examination of the Oil Utilized in Manual Transmissions\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Strict attention to detail is required during the production of manual transmission oil to ensure that it provides the utmost level of efficiency and protection. Manual gearbox lubricants, as opposed to engine oils, are necessary to fulfill the particular demands of gear operation. The capability to operate under high shear forces and the prohibition of metal-on-metal contact are among these requirements. There is a potential origin for these oils in advanced synthetic formulations, including polyalphaolefins, renowned for their exceptional durability and stability.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"One of the critical factors influencing the performance of manual gearbox oil is its exceptional thermal stability, as evidenced by its high viscosity index (indicating minimal temperature-induced viscosity variation) and ability to retain its protective properties despite exposure to elevated temperatures. Additionally, resistance to oxidation is critical because it contributes to the gearbox’s structural integrity and extends the oil’s service life.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In regard to environmental impact, synthetic gearbox oils are demonstrating noteworthy advancements in reducing their ecological imprint. By increasing fuel efficiency and extending service intervals, these lubricants ultimately reduce the amount of residual oil produced and the amount of resources consumed over time. Additionally, certain formulations prioritize biodegradability and recyclability, which is consistent with the goals of global sustainability.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"International Research and Development Regarding Manual Transmission\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In lubricant technology, ongoing investigations concerning manual transmission lubricants persistently expand the boundaries of what remains feasible. An additional innovation that has been incorporated is the development of novel additive packages, which are specifically engineered to mitigate lubricant wear and prolong its lifespan. An investigation is currently underway to examine the potential of these lubricants to enhance the overall efficacy of a vehicle, in addition to their interactions with recently developed gearbox materials and designs.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The outcomes of such investigations inform the formulation of industry benchmarks, which in turn are influencing the adjustment of maintenance protocols to include lubricants that offer enhanced environmental protection and prolonged service life. Regulations are also being impacted by these developments, given the worldwide pursuit of products that not only exhibit enhanced performance but also minimize environmental harm.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"A Distinction Analysis of the Products Offered by Atlantic Manual Transmission Oil \"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"An analysis of the gear oil manual transmission fluid provided by Atlantic reveals that the organization adopts a targeted strategy with regard to lubrication. Their high-performance oils are engineered to withstand the most extreme operating temperatures while providing the utmost protection for racing gearboxes, in order to satisfy their stringent requirements. The utmost importance is placed on load-bearing capacity and thermal stability in their heavy-duty industrial machinery. This practice guarantees the machinery’s sustained and dependable operation during periods of continuous operation.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"With regards to performance and cost-effectiveness, Atlantic’s portfolio provides clients with the option to select a solution that not only adheres to their financial constraints but also provides the utmost level of security for their specific use case. This guarantees that their equipment will continue to operate without any complications for an extended duration.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic Grease & Lubricants produces best manual transmission fluid that represent the highest standard of lubricant engineering. These lubricants are formulated to satisfy the rigorous specifications of contemporary gearboxes across numerous industries. We cordially invite you to peruse our assortment of lubricating solutions in an effort to identify the one that best meets your needs. Please feel free to consult our website for further details or contact us for personalized assistance.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic Trans HD\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC TRANS HD is a heavy-duty vehicle and machinery lubricant that is frequently used in abrasive environments such as mines, construction sites, and farms. Caterpillar, a large corporation renowned for its robust machinery, has established extremely stringent quality standards for this oil. As a result, it is designed to function exceptionally well with specific types of gearboxes and components that aid machines in shifting gears effortlessly.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The lubricant is formulated with specialized components that safeguard machines against deterioration, even under extreme conditions or when they are operating at maximum capacity. It is advantageous for machinery that must manage substantial loads and for those equipped with hydraulic systems, which are frequently employed to mobilize components such as spades or arms.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Additionally, ATLANTIC TRANS HD is designed to prevent corrosion and to prevent the oil from decomposing when heated. It also operates effectively in cold weather, preventing the oil from solidifying and remaining fluid, allowing the apparatus to start and operate without difficulty. This oil is highly recommended for the most demanding tasks and for lubricating and protecting the moving parts of this enormous machinery.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic Top Gear Oils EP\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC TOP GEAR OILS EP are specialized oils designed to safeguard the gearbox of your vehicle—the component that enables you to shift gears while traveling. These lubricants are not ordinary oils; they are formulated with extra-strength components to withstand high pressure and prevent internal gearbox damage, thereby extending their life.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Consider a vehicle such as a car or truck traversing rough terrain or towing heavy cargo; this oil prevents the gears from grinding against one another. Comparable to a superhero shield, it prevents the gears from deteriorating despite extreme stress. This oil maintains its consistency in viscosity even when the temperature outside is extreme, so it functions well throughout the year.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"This oil does not require as frequent of an oil change as others do, saving you both time and money. Additionally, it is safe for use with a variety of materials within the vehicle, including metal gears and rubber gaskets, and it reduces the likelihood of rust or oil bubble formation on components.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC asserts that this oil satisfies a multitude of critical criteria, which is why major automakers rely on it for their large trucks and equipment. Its multitude of advantages for maintaining the transmission of your vehicle is highly advantageous, rendering it a judicious selection for individuals who prioritize vehicle maintenance and desire to circumvent frequent visits to the mechanic.\"}]}]','2024-08-15 06:23:16.177000','2024-08-15 06:23:16.177000',NULL,2,2,'2024-05-15'),(19,'How Evolving Automotive Coolant Technologies Are Meeting the Demands of Modern Vehicles','how-evolving-automotive-coolant-technologies-are-meeting-the-demands-of-modern-vehicles','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The market for \"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"url\":\"https://atlanticlubes.com/product/atlantic-radiator-coolant/\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"automotive coolants\",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is changing because cars are getting better with a series of models backed by technology and the demand of the hour. People want coolants that last longer and work better with their car’s engines. These days, automobiles have smaller, more powerful engines that heat up more quickly. These engines need high-tech cooling fluids that can get rid of heat quickly and protect against rust well.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"To meet these needs, the car industry is switching to coolants with additives and inhibitors that make them last longer and resist corrosion. Fluids based on organic acid technology (OAT) and hybrid organic acid technology (HOAT) are slowly taking the place of traditional green coolants that are based on inorganic additive technology (IAT). Leading automakers like General Motors and Ford suggest OAT coolants because they protect modern engines with aluminum parts better.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Factors That Are Influencing Coolant Adoption Trends\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The switch to newer coolant systems is affected by things like the economy, the age of the vehicles, and how they are maintained in different areas. In developed countries, OAT and HOAT coolants are becoming more popular. However, older cars in price-sensitive markets still use traditional IAT coolants.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Also, the growing number of electric cars (EVs) is leading to new coolant formulas. Managing heat is important for electric vehicles, and new cooling technologies are being created to make batteries work better and be safer.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Because car engines are getting advanced in technology and performance, but this is not limited to this only. People are now buying electric cars, and the coolant business is going through a big change. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"So to make new cooling solutions will become even more important as environmental rules get stricter and car designs keep getting better. This is to make sure that cars run well and last a long time.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Some places around the world use more modern coolants at inexpensive prices than other fluids. The average age of cars, customer tastes, and how often people fix their cars can all have an effect on the fluid market. For example, traditional coolants with synthetic ingredients are still used a lot in India and Mexico, two growing countries with older car fleets. Most people in these places are very careful about how much they spend, so the older coolants are chosen over the newer ones because they are more affordable.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Rise of Tech-Driven Coolant Technologies\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Advanced coolants based on organic acid technology (OAT) and hybrid OAT (HOAT), on the other hand, are quickly becoming popular in wealthy countries where people care about the environment and have better cars. These coolants work better and last longer, which is what modern engines need and what tighter environmental rules require.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"This is because engines need to run better, need to be serviced less often, and need to have less of an impact on the environment.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It is now common in rich countries like the US and UK to use new coolants made with organic acids. We call these OAT coolants. New cars with engines made of metal parts work really well with these coolants. For their newest cars, big names like General Motors and Ford recommend OAT coolants because they work better.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"A Relative Analysis of OAT and HOAT Coolants with Performance and Longevity\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"A-Relative-Analysis-of-OAT-and-HOAT-Coolants-with-Performance-and-Longevity (1).jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"A-Relative-Analysis-of-OAT-and-HOAT-Coolants-with-Performance-and-Longevity (1).jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/A_Relative_Analysis_of_OAT_and_HOAT_Coolants_with_Performance_and_Longevity_1_8cd8fd9f49.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1200,\"height\":600,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_A-Relative-Analysis-of-OAT-and-HOAT-Coolants-with-Performance-and-Longevity (1).jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_A_Relative_Analysis_of_OAT_and_HOAT_Coolants_with_Performance_and_Longevity_1_8cd8fd9f49\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":123,\"size\":11.14,\"sizeInBytes\":11144,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_A_Relative_Analysis_of_OAT_and_HOAT_Coolants_with_Performance_and_Longevity_1_8cd8fd9f49.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_A-Relative-Analysis-of-OAT-and-HOAT-Coolants-with-Performance-and-Longevity (1).jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_A_Relative_Analysis_of_OAT_and_HOAT_Coolants_with_Performance_and_Longevity_1_8cd8fd9f49\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":100.79,\"sizeInBytes\":100790,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_A_Relative_Analysis_of_OAT_and_HOAT_Coolants_with_Performance_and_Longevity_1_8cd8fd9f49.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_A-Relative-Analysis-of-OAT-and-HOAT-Coolants-with-Performance-and-Longevity (1).jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_A_Relative_Analysis_of_OAT_and_HOAT_Coolants_with_Performance_and_Longevity_1_8cd8fd9f49\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":35.12,\"sizeInBytes\":35122,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_A_Relative_Analysis_of_OAT_and_HOAT_Coolants_with_Performance_and_Longevity_1_8cd8fd9f49.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_A-Relative-Analysis-of-OAT-and-HOAT-Coolants-with-Performance-and-Longevity (1).jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_A_Relative_Analysis_of_OAT_and_HOAT_Coolants_with_Performance_and_Longevity_1_8cd8fd9f49\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":65.7,\"sizeInBytes\":65697,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_A_Relative_Analysis_of_OAT_and_HOAT_Coolants_with_Performance_and_Longevity_1_8cd8fd9f49.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"A_Relative_Analysis_of_OAT_and_HOAT_Coolants_with_Performance_and_Longevity_1_8cd8fd9f49\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":174.85,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-10-01T11:06:35.412Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-10-01T11:06:35.412Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Several natural coolants, including sebacate and 2-EHA, are used in OAT oils. Like most coolants, they don\'t have silicates or phosphates in them. Longer-lasting metal and cast-iron engine parts are made with these ingredients.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"You can use OAT coolants in heavy-duty vehicles for up to three years or 500,000 kilometers. You can use them in light-duty vehicles for up to 150,000 miles or five years. This is because they are made to last. These days, OAT coolants are better for cars because they protect the engine for longer and don\'t need to be changed as often.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"People who make cars in Asia like to use HOAT coolants. These coolants have organic acids and other chemicals in them but not as much silicate as older coolants did. HOAT coolants can last up to five years or 150,000 miles in passenger cars. Heavy-duty trucks can use them for up to three years or 500,000 km. The big coolant makers in China, like Sinopec and CNPC, are all making HOAT coolants at the moment.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Adoption of Advanced Coolants in Developed Countries\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Germany and Japan, both of which have strong economies, are using Si-OAT and PHOAT new types of coolants for the first time.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Organic acids are used to make Si-OAT coolants, which also add silicates for extra safety. They work great for aluminum engines that are under a lot of pressure and need a lot of security. PHOAT coolants work like HOAT coolants, but they use phosphate instead of silicate. Volkswagen, Mercedes-Benz, and Volvo are all German car makers that use Si-OAT coolants. Japan\'s Ford, Toyota, and Subaru are all car companies that use PHOAT coolants.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Newer organic coolants are fully used in developed countries, but they are taking longer to catch on in developing countries.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In developing countries, people are still very price careful, so Si-OAT and PHOAT coolants aren\'t used very often. Most of the time, these new coolants cost 1.5 to 2 times as much as regular ones, which means that people on a budget can\'t afford to buy them.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Impact of Electric Vehicles on Coolant Technology\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It is also important to make changes to coolant because electric cars (EVs) are becoming more common. People worldwide like electric cars more and more, and the market for them is growing quickly. To be safe, EVs need temperature control systems. These systems also help the batteries last longer, and the cars can go farther. Because of this, carmakers are working on new ways to keep the temperature inside electric vehicles (EVs) under control. There is cooling by air, cooling by liquid that comes from another source, and direct cooling by liquid or absorption.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Direct cooling methods are used in most electric cars these days. This means that water doesn\'t touch the batteries directly. These coolants are mixed with water 50/50 because water moves heat around well. Not all EVs use air cooling. The Nissan LEAF, the Wuling Mini EV, and some Japanese types still do. The small batteries in these cars only need air cooling to stay at the right temperature.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Future of Coolant Technology-Immersion Cooling\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"The-Future-of-Coolant-Technology-Immersion-Cooling (1).jpg\",\"alternativeText\":\"The-Future-of-Coolant-Technology-Immersion-Cooling (1).jpg\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/The_Future_of_Coolant_Technology_Immersion_Cooling_1_b18a3b090a.jpg\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1200,\"height\":600,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_The-Future-of-Coolant-Technology-Immersion-Cooling (1).jpg\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_The_Future_of_Coolant_Technology_Immersion_Cooling_1_b18a3b090a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":123,\"size\":7.63,\"sizeInBytes\":7632,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_The_Future_of_Coolant_Technology_Immersion_Cooling_1_b18a3b090a.jpg\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_The-Future-of-Coolant-Technology-Immersion-Cooling (1).jpg\",\"hash\":\"medium_The_Future_of_Coolant_Technology_Immersion_Cooling_1_b18a3b090a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":50.03,\"sizeInBytes\":50033,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_The_Future_of_Coolant_Technology_Immersion_Cooling_1_b18a3b090a.jpg\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_The-Future-of-Coolant-Technology-Immersion-Cooling (1).jpg\",\"hash\":\"small_The_Future_of_Coolant_Technology_Immersion_Cooling_1_b18a3b090a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":25.46,\"sizeInBytes\":25458,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_The_Future_of_Coolant_Technology_Immersion_Cooling_1_b18a3b090a.jpg\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_The-Future-of-Coolant-Technology-Immersion-Cooling (1).jpg\",\"hash\":\"large_The_Future_of_Coolant_Technology_Immersion_Cooling_1_b18a3b090a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":78.83,\"sizeInBytes\":78833,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_The_Future_of_Coolant_Technology_Immersion_Cooling_1_b18a3b090a.jpg\"}},\"hash\":\"The_Future_of_Coolant_Technology_Immersion_Cooling_1_b18a3b090a\",\"ext\":\".jpg\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"size\":141.11,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2024-10-01T11:08:17.677Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-10-01T11:08:17.677Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Immersion cooling is the third way to cool something down. To use this method, the EV battery is put in a special liquid that doesn\'t let electricity flow through it. Most private cars still need to start using this technology because it is still being tested and worked on. Immersion cooling is still popular, but more and more people opt for electric and fuel cars.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When it comes to making immersion cooling technology for electric vehicles (EVs), there has yet to be a clear leader. A number of new businesses of advanced lubrication specialties are coming up with creative ways to cool EV batteries while they are submerged. Xing Mobility, a Taiwanese company that makes immersion cooling systems for EV batteries, is a good example of this. Xing Mobility offers a wide range of battery options for electric vehicles, such as modular battery packs that use immersion cooling technology. The business just recently teamed up with other brands to improve its immersion cooling battery pack technology for electric vehicles. Immersion cooling is becoming more popular as a possible way to keep EVs cool, and this partnership shows that.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Impact of Environmental Regulations on Coolant Technology\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"To sum up, if we want to make transportation more eco-friendly, we need to change the way coolants work. Tougher rules about the environment are causing changes in how cars are made, like making them lighter, using different materials, adding more technology, and making more electric cars. Because of these changes, a car\'s cooling system and, by extension, the coolants inside it have to work harder.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The automotive coolant business is about to go through a big change because cooling systems are becoming more and more important for making cars more efficient. At the moment, most of the work is going into making indirect cooling technology for both gas-powered and electric cars. However, this method might only work for EVs for a short time. For a long time, the common automotive engine coolants are still powerful. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"As the demand for electric and fuel-cell cars grows, the industry is also on the verge of a possible breakthrough in immersion cooling technology. EV batteries are directly immersed in a special non-conductive fluid as part of this new way to cool them down. This method offers better heat reduction and may even extend the life of the batteries.Because of these improvements, cooling technology is likely to change a lot in the next ten years, making it an interesting area to keep an eye on. As cars become more electric and environmentally friendly, the new \"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"url\":\"https://atlanticlubes.com/product-category/automotive-specialties/\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"best automotive specialty\",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" will play a big role in determining how well and how efficiently cars run in the future.\"}]}]','2024-10-01 11:08:40.212000','2024-10-01 11:08:42.734000','2024-10-01 11:08:42.730000',2,2,'2024-10-01'),(20,'Top Automotive Specialty Products in High Demand in the UAE','top-automotive-specialty-products-in-high-demand-in-the-uae','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The automobile industry is booming in the UAE. The increased number of luxury cars is leading to a high demand for specialized car care products that help keep vehicles running well and protect them from severe weather conditions. This article will cover the top specialty automotive products in the automotive specialty market in the UAE and why they are necessary.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"1. High-performance engine oils\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Cars in the UAE require some high-performance engine oils because of the hot climate under which the engines are prone to overheating and wear up quickly. These oils also stop friction and cool their engines, hence protecting the engines from wearing out. They are manufactured synthetically, as they are derived from chemical components rather than oil sources in nature. \"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"url\":\"https://atlanticlubes.com/\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Synthetic lubricants\",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" work better with increased temperatures. Thus many car owners in the UAE use them.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The right type of engine oil improves fuel efficiency and extends the life of the engine. Also, it makes the engine run more smoothly, which is very important for covering long distances in the desert or busy city traffic. Many UAE car owners prefer premium brands because of better protection in extreme heat.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"2. Coolants and Antifreeze\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Coolants are also referred to as antifreeze. Coolants are liquids that absorb heat from a car\'s engine and prevent the engine from heating up too much. They help pass the absorbed heat out by releasing it once the liquid passes through the cooling system. In such a hot country as the UAE, coolants play a big role because they prevent the engines from heating up to extreme temperatures.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The high temperatures in the UAE make it very hard for any engine to cool itself down. This can significantly damage an engine, therefore expensive repairs to the car. This has made most UAE drivers look for excellent coolants suitable for such extremely hot climatic conditions. The fluids also keep rust from forming on engines and the cooling system and ensure there is no corrosion.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"3. Transmission Fluids\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"These special oils keep the transmission of a car going. The transmission is a crucial part of any vehicle since it changes the gears, which makes the car go faster or slower. Good transmission fluid is, therefore, a must for any car in the UAE where extreme conditions are experienced.\"}]},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Transmission-Fluids.png\",\"alternativeText\":\"Transmission Fluids\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Transmission_Fluids_b6018e590f.png\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1200,\"height\":600,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Transmission-Fluids.png\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Transmission_Fluids_b6018e590f\",\"ext\":\".png\",\"mime\":\"image/png\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":123,\"size\":55.28,\"sizeInBytes\":55280,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Transmission_Fluids_b6018e590f.png\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Transmission-Fluids.png\",\"hash\":\"small_Transmission_Fluids_b6018e590f\",\"ext\":\".png\",\"mime\":\"image/png\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":208.21,\"sizeInBytes\":208214,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Transmission_Fluids_b6018e590f.png\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Transmission-Fluids.png\",\"hash\":\"medium_Transmission_Fluids_b6018e590f\",\"ext\":\".png\",\"mime\":\"image/png\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":442.24,\"sizeInBytes\":442243,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Transmission_Fluids_b6018e590f.png\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Transmission-Fluids.png\",\"hash\":\"large_Transmission_Fluids_b6018e590f\",\"ext\":\".png\",\"mime\":\"image/png\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":748.08,\"sizeInBytes\":748076,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Transmission_Fluids_b6018e590f.png\"}},\"hash\":\"Transmission_Fluids_b6018e590f\",\"ext\":\".png\",\"mime\":\"image/png\",\"size\":593.87,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2025-01-02T06:54:47.725Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2025-01-02T06:54:47.725Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The hot climate causes the breakdown of the transmission fluid. This breakdown affects the performance of the transmission. In high-quality transmission fluids, there is the ability to counter high temperatures and protect transmissions from wear and tear. These fluids also reduce the friction that occurs within a transmission. This enables a smooth shift of gears as the quality of the fluids is enhanced. Quality fluid for transmissions prevents UAE vehicle owners from experiencing transmission faults and helps extend the period of usage of their automobiles.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"4. Brake Fluids\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Brake fluids are the liquids through which a car\'s braking system is made to function. It is when the driver applies pressure on the brake pedal that the fluid transfers this force to the brakes to slow down or stop the car. For the traffic conditions in the UAE and high temperatures, good brake fluid is therefore necessary.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Brake fluids break down much faster in extremely hot temperatures in the UAE, which makes the brakes feel less responsive. It can boil brake fluid if it gets too hot. However, some brake fluids are made to withstand hot temperatures, ensuring that the brakes stay responsive and safe to use. Most UAE drivers prefer brake fluids that can provide better heat resistance to keep their braking systems reliable.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"5. Air filters\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Air filters are among the important parts that make car engines clean. This is because they prevent sand and dust from reaching your engine. This is key in the UAE because of the common conditions of sand and dusty surroundings. Engines get dirty so fast if the conditions are dirty. An engine makes the performance of a vehicle decline, thus requiring more fuel.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It has a high-quality air filter, which filters more dirt and dust. This keeps the engine much cleaner for a long period. Cleaner engines move efficiently and last longer; therefore, the demand for good-quality air filters in the UAE is high. People are advised to change their filters often to ensure that they keep their engines clean in the harsh desert weather.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"6. Battery Maintainers\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Car batteries in the UAE face quite hostile conditions. Indeed, the heat drains the batteries much faster than they would be used up in a cool climate. A battery maintainer is an apparatus that keeps the car battery charged and in the best condition possible. They monitor the charge and supply power when it has run low, thus readying the battery for use whenever you need it.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Its most helpful advantage is the prevention of the failure of a car\'s battery at an unfavorable moment. This is greatly relevant to the UAE environment since many people use cars daily and drive long miles now and then for recreation. People, especially those who rarely use cars, would benefit from them because these devices could help ensure that the cars remained fit with healthy batteries as they hardly ever used them.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"7. Fuel additives\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Fuel additives are chemicals added to gasoline and help improve the performance of a car. They clean out the engine, reduce harmful emissions, and increase efficiency. In the UAE, driving long distances is often practiced, and fuel additives are popular for keeping their engines in good condition.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Fuel additives prevent engine deposits. These are the buildups that happen over time, making engines work harder. Keeping the engine cleaner saves cars from using much fuel, which will eventually cut down on money spent on fuel by drivers. This also reduces harmful emissions and is a good choice for environmentally conscious drivers.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"8. Wax and Paint Protection\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Intensive sunshine in the UAE easily damages the paint of a car. UV rays lead to fading of paint, and the car is left looking old. Protecting wax and paint are used on the outer surfaces to create a protective coat. This effect reflects sunlight and prevents fading, making the car look new for longer.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Wax and paint protection also guard the car against sand and dust. If not washed off, these particles may scratch the paint. Good-quality waxes and sealants give a smooth surface, making it hard for dirt to stick to the car. Most of the car owners in the UAE use these products on a regular basis to maintain their vehicles despite the extreme weather conditions.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"9. Tire Protection and Sealants\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The roads and grounds of the UAE are mostly hot and rugged, exposing the tires to this type of condition constantly. Such a condition leads to rapid wearing out of the tires and increases the chance of getting punctured. Protection products and sealants help protect the tires from this type of situation by providing additional durability to the tires.\"}]},{\"type\":\"image\",\"image\":{\"name\":\"Tire-Protection-and-Sealants.png\",\"alternativeText\":\"Tire Protection and Sealants\",\"url\":\"https://admin.atlanticlubes.com/uploads/Tire_Protection_and_Sealants_fa72354f17.png\",\"caption\":null,\"width\":1200,\"height\":600,\"formats\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"name\":\"thumbnail_Tire-Protection-and-Sealants.png\",\"hash\":\"thumbnail_Tire_Protection_and_Sealants_fa72354f17\",\"ext\":\".png\",\"mime\":\"image/png\",\"path\":null,\"width\":245,\"height\":123,\"size\":62.99,\"sizeInBytes\":62985,\"url\":\"/uploads/thumbnail_Tire_Protection_and_Sealants_fa72354f17.png\"},\"small\":{\"name\":\"small_Tire-Protection-and-Sealants.png\",\"hash\":\"small_Tire_Protection_and_Sealants_fa72354f17\",\"ext\":\".png\",\"mime\":\"image/png\",\"path\":null,\"width\":500,\"height\":250,\"size\":237.78,\"sizeInBytes\":237779,\"url\":\"/uploads/small_Tire_Protection_and_Sealants_fa72354f17.png\"},\"medium\":{\"name\":\"medium_Tire-Protection-and-Sealants.png\",\"hash\":\"medium_Tire_Protection_and_Sealants_fa72354f17\",\"ext\":\".png\",\"mime\":\"image/png\",\"path\":null,\"width\":750,\"height\":375,\"size\":507.96,\"sizeInBytes\":507959,\"url\":\"/uploads/medium_Tire_Protection_and_Sealants_fa72354f17.png\"},\"large\":{\"name\":\"large_Tire-Protection-and-Sealants.png\",\"hash\":\"large_Tire_Protection_and_Sealants_fa72354f17\",\"ext\":\".png\",\"mime\":\"image/png\",\"path\":null,\"width\":1000,\"height\":500,\"size\":863.67,\"sizeInBytes\":863674,\"url\":\"/uploads/large_Tire_Protection_and_Sealants_fa72354f17.png\"}},\"hash\":\"Tire_Protection_and_Sealants_fa72354f17\",\"ext\":\".png\",\"mime\":\"image/png\",\"size\":713.69,\"previewUrl\":null,\"provider\":\"local\",\"provider_metadata\":null,\"createdAt\":\"2025-01-02T06:57:28.782Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2025-01-02T06:57:28.782Z\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Sealants that self-seal small punctures reduce the chance of flat tires. For UAE motorists, particularly those traveling to desert roads where sharp rocks and debris abound, tire protection gives motorists more mileage on their tires and less time to replace them.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"10. Interior Conditioners and Protectants\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The interior of a car can degrade in the UAE\'s hot climatic conditions. The sun might crack or fade the seats and the dashboards with time. Interior conditioners and protectants are those products that protect the car\'s interior from heat and UV damage. They are applied on seats, dashboards, and other surfaces for protection against the sun.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"They have been in much demand in the UAE car market because of their property of giving the interior an appearance like a new vehicle. Moreover, they will not let the bad odors brought about by high temperatures and humidity. A car owner can ensure a fresh and comfortable interior if he makes use of this product during hot weather conditions.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In the UAE, \"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"url\":\"https://atlanticlubes.com/product-category/automotive-specialties/\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"automotive specialty products\",\"bold\":true}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" play a vital role in keeping vehicles in top shape. From engine oils to tire protection, the car faces the harsh climatic conditions of the country with such products. People in the UAE spend big money on the quality of specialty items, as they require a great ride and an extremely smooth and shiny appearance that lasts for years. As this demand is now common, it will soon come up with options to meet the requirements of specific drivers in the UAE. For any car owner interested in keeping a vehicle running in the UAE, proper specialty products go a long way.\"}]}]','2025-01-02 06:58:59.282000','2025-01-02 07:05:32.466000','2025-01-02 07:05:32.458000',2,2,'2025-01-02');
