ine life are all features of this product.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Excellent efficiency in the use of gasoline, an extension of the time between oil changes, and a reduction in the amount of oil added.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Good wear protection; excellent low temperature and easy starting; sometimes referred to as an all-weather oil.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"RECOMMENDATIONS / SPECIFICATIONS\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Approvals on an International Scale: API CJ-4, CI-4, CH-4/SN, ACEA E9 OEM Approvals: Volvo VDS-4\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"satisfies or outperforms the following specifications: MTU Type 2.1 Renault Trucks RDL-3 JASO DH-2 MAN 3575 CUMMINS 20081 CAT ECF -3 Mack EO-O Premium Plus MB – Approved 228.31 DDC 93K218\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It satisfies the quality criteria of the most recent heavy-duty diesel engines produced in the United States, Europe, and Japan, including those for difficult applications such as high loads and multi-trailer operations.\"}]}]','2024-08-29 07:37:07.277000','2025-01-15 06:07:22.177000',NULL,2,2,NULL,'SAE 15W 40','API CJ-4/E9',NULL,'ATLANTIC SYNTHECH TURBO'),(89,'ATLANTIC SUPER TOP FLEET HD-V DIESEL ENGINE OILS SAE 10W 40 API CK 4','atlantic-super-top-fleet-hd-v-diesel-engine-oils-ck-4','[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"DESCRIPTION\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC SUPER TOP FLEET HD-V DIESEL ENGINE OILS SAE 15W-40 and 10W-30 are innovative diesel engine oils that help extend engine life, which allows you to run your business with confidence. These diesel engine oils are available in two different viscosities: 15W-40 and 10W-30. These products give great performance in both on-highway and off-highway operations, and they meet or exceed the specifications set forth by original equipment manufacturers (OEM).\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC SUPER TOP FLEET HD-V DIESEL ENGINE OILS are fully backward compatible and give great performance in both modern and older heavy-duty engine designs. Because of this, the standards of the API CK-4, CJ-4, CI-4 PLUS, CI-4, and CH-4 service categories, as well as the needs of important OEMs, are satisfied or exceeded by the oils in question. ATLANTIC SUPER TOP FLEET HD-V DIESEL ENGINE OILS are universal, which means that in addition to being used in diesel engines, they may also be utilized in gasoline engines that call for the API SN specification.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC SUPER TOP FLEET HD-V DIESEL ENGINE OIL is a specially formulated product that provides superb wear and engine protection, exceptional high-temperature performance, extended drain capability, and engine cleanliness. They were developed in close collaboration with major original equipment manufacturers, and it is advised that they be used in a wide variety of heavy-duty applications and operating environments in the trucking, mining, construction, agricultural, and maritime industries.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"APPLICATIONS\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Highly recommended for use in modern heavy-duty diesel engines, such as those that feature after-treatment systems and EGR.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Suggested for use i