\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The use of caution is urged.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Get rid of the empty cans and recycle them.\"}]}]}]','2024-08-30 11:01:03.257000','2024-09-02 05:18:34.169000','2024-08-30 11:01:07.525000',2,2,NULL,'Spray and Tyre Shiner',NULL,NULL,'Atlantic Leather Protection'),(103,'Atlantic Hard Wax Car Polish','atlantic-hard-wax-car-polish','[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Atlantic Hard Wax – Car Care Polish\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Introducing the Atlantic Hard Wax – the ultimate car care solution for the discerning car owner! This carefully crafted hard wax is designed to create a thin and transparent layer of protection on your car’s paintwork, safeguarding it against the damaging effects of contaminants and other harmful elements. Its magic is instantaneous, instantly concealing any flaws and imbuing your car with a radiant shine that lasts and lasts. Give your car the ultimate pampering with Atlantic Hard Wax – your car deserves nothing less!\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Directions:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Thoroughly clean your car using mild soap and water and make sure it’s completely dry before applying wax.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Take a foam applicator or a damp sponge and apply a small amount of wax onto it.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Apply the wax in small, circular, overlapping strokes over a small section of the car (2 to 4 square feet at a time) to ensure even coverage.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Apply more wax as needed and buff out any imperfections.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Allow the wax to haze over before buffing it off.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Use a microfiber cloth to remove any excess wax and give your car a perfect polish.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Attention:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Do not apply wax to a car with a matte finish.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Work in a shaded area out of direct sunlight.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Storage:\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Keep out of the reach of the children.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Store away from heat or direct sunlight.\"}]}]}]','2024-08-30 11:12:49.996000','2024-09-02 05:19:00.989000','2024-08-30 11:12:55.449000',2,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Atlantic Hard Wax Car Polish'),(104,'Atlantic Windscreen Cleaner Concentrate','atlantic-windscreen-cleaner-concentrate','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Windscreen Cleaner Concentrate is a highly effective cleaning concentrate which has been specially formulated for vehicle windscreen washer systems as well for manual cleaning of vehicle windows.\"}]}