\":\"ATLANTIC SYNTHECH MULTI-VEHICLE ATF FE is a technologically advanced, fully synthetic lubricant based on carefully selected, very highly refined base oils for automatic transmissions with a high viscosity index, excellent oxidation stability, excellent friction and antiwear properties providing maximum fuel efficiency for modern automatic transmissions and meeting the requirements of most American, Japanese and European manufacturers.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Applications\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC SYNTHECH MULTI-VEHICLE ATF is suitable for use in the latest generations of automatic transmissions and torque convertors for most passenger cars, off-road vehicles and SUVs.  Meets or exceeds the requirements of the JASO-1A performance standard and the latest ATF specifications of Ford and GM for use in vehicles.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Properties\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC SYNTHECH MULTI-VEHICLE ATF FE is high quality ATF fluid ensuring superior low temperature performance, easy pumpability and improved cold start. It has excellent frictional properties and performs exceptionally well in reducing sludge and preventing the formation of deposits.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Performance Features And Benefits\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Anti-wear protection: significantly extended transmission life.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Extended oil life: excellent thermal and oxidation stability.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":