d as the original fluid in VW, BMW, MB and other makes), level control, shock absorbers, hydro-pneumatic springs, stability and traction systems, electri- cal/hydraulic convertible roof controls, central locking systems, etc.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Performance Features And Benefits\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Synthetic base stock blends insure exceptional performance throughout a wide temperature range\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Prevents high temperature thinning and “afternoon fade”, even on long hot summer days\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Exceptional functionality in low temperatures, ensuring efficient oil delivery to the system during cold conditions\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Improves pump efficiency & increases productivity by as much as 30% or more over conventional hydraulic oils\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"All-temperature formula eliminates seasonal changes\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Suitable for use in temperatures down to -40°C\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Remarkable resistance to oxidation and aging\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Superior protection against corrosion and wea