itions.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Recommendations/Specifications\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Meets or exceeds: MAN Diesel &Turbo, MHI-MME and Wärtsilä, Mitsubishi Heavy Industries.\"}]}]','2025-05-16 06:36:03.819000','2025-05-24 09:05:52.413000','2025-05-16 06:36:05.670000',2,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Atlantic Marine Cylinder Oils'),(214,'Atlantic Marine System Oils','atlantic-marine-system-oils','[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Marine Crankcase Lubricant\",\"italic\":true}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC MARINE SYSTEM OILS are marine oils especially designed for the crankcase lubrication of slow speed 2 stroke crosshead Diesel engines & also suitable for plain bearings of turbochargers, shaft bearings, stern tube and seals. The formulation has maximum antiwear properties, good rust protection in the presence of salt water, and excellent water separation characteristics.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Applications\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC MARINE SYSTEM OILS are designed for Crankshaft lubrication, cooled pistons & Shaft bearing lubrication. Primarily recommended for use as system oil in late model, high-output, crosshead diesel engines, especially those engines employing the system oil for piston cooling. It will prevent or reduce deposit formation in the piston cooling spaces, thus maintaining piston cooling efficiency and reducing the incidence of piston top burning and piston crown cracking. It will also prevent or reduce crankcase deposits and will provide outstanding protection for heavily loaded bearings.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Properties\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC MARINE SYSTEM OILS have been particularly formulated from high quality paraffinic base oils along with a balanced additive system to provide excellent protection even for the severe operating conditions of the latest design, high-output crosshead marine diesel engines. In addition, the alkalinity is sufficient to neutralize crankcase contaminations or acidic combustion products in a less demanding four-stroke trunk piston diesel engine running on distillate fuel.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Performance Features And Benefits\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Very good detergency level.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Very good thermal stability.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Very good anti-oxidant characteristics.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Excellent anti-rust and anti-corrosive properties.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Clean crankcase.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Excellent capacity for water separation.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Excellent capacity for insoluble separation.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Good anti-wear properties.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"