0 are designed for conditions of moderate oil stress.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC TP X 40040 is designed for conditions of high oil stress and has been formulated to help improve deposit control. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC TP XL 40050 is designed for conditions of very high oil stress and has been further optimized to improve deposit control.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Properties\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ATLANTIC TRUNK PISTON ENGINE OILS combines an exclusive formulation of latest additive technologies and highly refined base oils to provide a substantial safety margin to cope with the higher stress levels even with the latest and future designs of diesel engines. Particularly suitable for low or very low oil consumption engines operating with a poor quality residual fuel.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Performance Features And Benefits\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Excellent resistance to the negative effects of contamination with residual fuel.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Excellent thermal resistance and high temperature oxidation resistance.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Excellent control of viscosity increase leading to reduced top-ups.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Very good wear protection and very good oil film strength at extreme pressures.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"