s to provide good lubrication and a higher degree of fire resistance.\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"PERFORMANCE FEATURES AND BENEFITS\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Lower flammability than mineral oils.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Readily biodegradable\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Low ecotoxicity - ‘not harmful’ to plants,invertebrates and fish\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Excellent viscosity/temperature characteristics\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Low flammability maintained during the life of the fluid.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Excellent corrosion protection.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Compatible with most materials specified for use with mineral oils.\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list\",\"format\":\"unordered\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"list-item\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Pump anti-wear protection similar to mineral hydraulic oils\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"RECOMMENDATIONS / SPECIFICATIONS\"}],\"level\":2},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ISO 6743/4 HFDU, ISO 12922, DIN 51502 HFDU\"}]}]','2025-05-24 07:20:31.982000','2025-05-26 11:55:05.042000','2025-05-24 07:21:52.806000',2,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'ATLANTI